<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lds&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregister </eesti>
<inglise>Estonian Central Register of Securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregister (edaspidi register) on register aktsiate, v&otilde;lakohustuste ja muude k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 2 nimetatud &otilde;iguste (edaspidi v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid) ja nende &otilde;igustega tehtavate toimingute registreerimiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Estonian Central Register of Securities (hereinafter register) is a register for the registration of shares, debt obligations and other rights specified in &sect; 2 of this Act (hereinafter securities) and operations performed with such rights. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registrile ja selle pidamisele ei kohaldata andmekogude seadust (RT I 1997, 28, 423; 1998, 36/37, 552; 1999, 10, 155; 2000, 50, 317; 57, 373; 92, 597; 2001, 7, 17; 17, 77; 24, 133), kui k&auml;esolevast seadusest ei tulene teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Databases Act (RT I 1997, 28, 423; 1998, 36/37, 552; 1999, 10, 155; 2000, 50, 317; 57, 373; 92, 597; 2001, 7, 17; 17, 77; 24, 133) does not apply to the register and maintenance thereof unless otherwise provided by this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Registri ese </eesti>
<inglise>Objects of register </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registris peavad olema registreeritud j&auml;rgmised &otilde;igused ja kohustused: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The following rights and obligations shall be entered in the register: </inglise>
<eesti>1) Eesti Vabariigi, Eesti Vabariigi kohalike omavalitsus&uuml;ksuste ning muude avalik-&otilde;iguslike juriidiliste isikute poolt emiteeritud v&otilde;lakohustused; </eesti>
<inglise>1) debt obligations issued by the Republic of Estonia, the local governments of the Republic of Estonia and other legal persons in public law; </inglise>
<eesti>2) Eestis registreeritud era&otilde;iguslike juriidiliste isikute poolt emiteeritud v&otilde;lakohustused, mis kuuluvad v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru seaduse (RT I 1993, 35, 543; 1995, 22, 328; 1996, 26, 528; 1997, 34, 535; 1998, 61, 979; 2000, 10, 55) kohaselt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberij&auml;relevalves registreerimisele avaliku emissiooni v&otilde;i avaliku pakkumisena; </eesti>
<inglise>2) debt obligations issued by legal persons in private law registered in Estonia if, pursuant to the Securities Market Act (RT I 1993, 35, 543; 1995, 22, 328; 1996, 26, 528; 1997, 34, 535; 1998, 61, 979; 2000, 10, 55), such obligations are subject to registration with the securities supervision authority as a public issue or public tender; </inglise>
<eesti>3) Eestis registreeritud aktsiaseltsi aktsiad; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the shares of public limited companies registered in Estonia; </inglise>
<eesti>4) Eestis registreeritud investeerimisfondide aktsiad ja osakud; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the shares and units of investment funds registered in Estonia; </inglise>
<eesti>5) aktsiate ja registris registreerimisele kuuluvate avalikult emiteeritud v&otilde;i avalikult pakutavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite m&auml;rkimis&otilde;igused. </eesti>
<inglise>5) subscription rights for shares, and for securities subject to entry in the register which are publicly issued or publicly tendered. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Lisaks k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud &otilde;igustele ja kohustustele v&otilde;ib registris registreerida teisi aktsiaid, m&auml;rkimis&otilde;igusi, osasid ja emiteeritud v&otilde;lakohustusi ning muid sarnaseid &otilde;igusi ja kohustusi, kui seadusega ei s&auml;testata teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In addition to the rights and obligations specified in subsection (1) of this section, other shares, subscription rights, issued debt obligations and other similar rights and obligations may be entered in the register unless otherwise provided by this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Auml;ri&uuml;hingu aktsiad v&otilde;i osad v&otilde;ib registris registreerida &uuml;ksnes aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali t&auml;ies ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The shares of a company may be entered in the register only in the full amount of the share capital. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri pidajal (edaspidi registripidaja) on k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimise ainu&otilde;igus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar of the Estonian Central Register of Securities (hereinafter registrar) holds the sale right to register securities specified in subsection (1) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Registrisse kantavad andmed </eesti>
<inglise>Information Subject to Entry in Register </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Registri struktuur </eesti>
<inglise>Structure of Register </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registrit peetakse j&auml;rgmiste andmete kohta: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The following information shall be entered in the register: </inglise>
<eesti>1) emitendid, nende emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanikud (aktsiaraamat, osanike nimekiri vms); </eesti>
<inglise>1) issuers, securities issued thereby and the owners of the securities (share registers, lists of shareholders, etc); </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omanikud ja neile kuuluvad v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid (v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontod); </eesti>
<inglise>2) owners of securities and securities owned thereby (securities accounts); </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omandamine, v&otilde;&otilde;randamine ja pantimine. </eesti>
<inglise>3) acquisitions, transfers and pledges of securities. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registrisse kantakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-des 4 ja 5 nimetatud ning muud rahandusministri poolt m&auml;&auml;ratud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Information specified in &sect;&sect; 4 and 5 of this Act and other information determined by the Minister of Finance shall be entered in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmed emitendi ja tema emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta </eesti>
<inglise>Information concerning issuers and securities issued thereby </inglise>
<eesti>Emitendi ja tema emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta kantakse registrisse j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>The following information shall be entered in the register with regard to an issuer and the securities issued thereby: </inglise>
<eesti>1) emitendi nimi, asukoht ja v&otilde;imaluse korral registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name, seat and, if possible, registry code of the issuer; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite liik, nimiv&auml;&auml;rtus (koos v&auml;&auml;ringuga) ja kogus; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the type, nominal value (including currency) and amount of the securities; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omanike nimed, aadressid ja isiku- v&otilde;i registrikoodid, isikukoodi puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the names, addresses, and personal identification codes or registry codes of the owners of the securities and, in the absence of a personal identification code, the date of birth; </inglise>
<eesti>4) andmed v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite pantimise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>4) information concerning pledges of securities. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto </eesti>
<inglise>Securities account </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&otilde;ib registris avada igale Eesti v&otilde;i v&auml;lisriigi isikule. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A securities account in the register may be opened for any Estonian or foreign person. </inglise>
<eesti>Isikul v&otilde;ib olla mitu v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontot. </eesti>
<inglise>A person may have several securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Lepingulise investeerimisfondi jaoks avatakse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto fondivalitseja taotlusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A securities account for a contractual investment fund shall be opened at the request of the management company of the fund. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Isikutele v&otilde;ib avada &uuml;hise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A joint securities account may be opened for several persons. </inglise>
<eesti>Sel juhul kuulub isikutele &uuml;hiselt igakordne v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto j&auml;&auml;k. </eesti>
<inglise>In such case, each particular balance of the securities account is owned by the persons jointly. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto kohta kantakse registrisse j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The following information shall be entered in the register with regard to a securities account: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku nimi; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name of the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the address of the owner of the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>3) f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku isikukood, selle puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) if the owner of the securities account is a natural person, his or her personal identification code or, in the absence thereof, date of birth; </inglise>
<eesti>4) juriidilisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku puhul viide registrile, kus juriidiline isik on registreeritud, ja registrikood, kui juriidiline isik on registreeritud; </eesti>
<inglise>4) if the owner of the securities account is a legal person, a reference to the register in which the legal person is registered, and the registry code if the legal person is registered; </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku pangakonto number registriga seotud arveldusi teostavas krediidiasutuses ja selle krediidiasutuse &auml;rinimi; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the number of the bank account held by the owner of the securities account in a credit institution which performs transactions relating to the register, and the business name of the credit institution; </inglise>
<eesti>6) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto number ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the number of the securities account and the date on which the securities account was opened; </inglise>
<eesti>7) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol olevate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kogus ja t&auml;histus; </eesti>
<inglise>7) the amount and denotation of the type of the securities in the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>8) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi mitmele isikule kuulumise korral v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi &uuml;histe omanike nimed, aadressid, isiku- v&otilde;i registrikoodid (isikukoodi puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg) ning kaasomandi korral iga kaasomaniku proportsionaalne osa v&auml;&auml;rtpaberist v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest; </eesti>
<inglise>8) if a security is owned by several persons, the names, addresses and personal identification codes or registry codes (or, in the absence of a personal identification code, the date of birth) of the owners and, in the case of common ownership, the proportional share of each co-owner in the security or securities; </inglise>
<eesti>9) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omandamise aeg ja muude kannete tegemise ajad; </eesti>
<inglise>9) the time of acquisition of the securities and the times at which other entries are made; </inglise>
<eesti>10) muud seadusega s&auml;testatud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>10) other information provided by law. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakonto </eesti>
<inglise>Nominee account </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselistel osalistel on &otilde;igus omada v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto eriliigina esindajakontot. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Professional participants in the Estonian securities market have the right to own a nominee account as a special type of securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakonto omamise &otilde;igus on ka v&auml;lismaistel juriidilistel isikutel v&otilde;i muudel institutsioonidel, kes vastavalt neile kohaldatavale seadusele v&otilde;ivad hoida v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid oma nimel ja teise isiku arvel. </eesti>
<inglise>Foreign legal persons and other institutions also have the right to own a nominee account if, according to the law applicable to them, they have the right to hold securities in their own name and on behalf of another person. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidamise korras v&otilde;ib esindajakonto avamiseks n&auml;ha esindajakonto omanikule ette t&auml;iendavaid n&otilde;udeid. </eesti>
<inglise>The procedure for maintenance of the register may prescribe additional requirements for owners of nominee accounts in the opening of the accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Esindajakonto vahendusel teostatakse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite valitsemist teise isiku (klient) jaoks ja arvel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Through a nominee account, securities are administered for and on behalf of another person (client). </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakontol v&otilde;ib hoida &uuml;ksnes niisuguseid v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid, mille omandamisel tegutseb esindajakonto omanik kliendi k&auml;sundi t&auml;itjana v&otilde;i muu sarnase suhte alusel, samuti esindajakontol hoitavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite tuluna saadud v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid. </eesti>
<inglise>The only securities which may be held in a nominee account are securities in the acquisition of which the owner of a nominee account acts as the mandatory of the client or on the basis of another similar relationship, and securities received as income from securities held in a nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>Muude v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite hoidmine esindajakontol on keelatud. </eesti>
<inglise>It is prohibited to hold other securities in a nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Esindajakonto omaniku poolt k&auml;sunduslepingu v&otilde;i muu sarnase lepingu alusel oma nimel, kuid kliendi arvel omandatud v&otilde;i esindajakonto omanikule lepingu t&auml;itmiseks &uuml;leantud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid loetakse esindajakonto omaniku ja tema v&otilde;lausaldajate suhtes kliendi v&auml;&auml;rtpaberiteks ning need ei kuulu esindajakonto omaniku pankrotivara hulka. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Securities acquired by the owner of a nominee account in the name of the owner but on behalf of a client on the basis of an authorisation agreement or other similar agreement, and securities transferred to the owner of a nominee account in order to execute an agreement are, with regard to the owner of the nominee account and the creditors thereof, deemed to be the securities of the client and they do not form part of the bankruptcy estate of the owner of the nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakonto omaniku vastu esitatud hagi tagamise abin&otilde;ud v&otilde;i muud esindajakonto omaniku suhtes riigi- v&otilde;i kohaliku omavalitsuse asutuse teostatava menetluse tagamiseks rakendatavad esindajakonto omaniku vara k&auml;sutuspiirangud ei h&otilde;lma esindajakontol olevaid kolmandatele isikutele kuuluvaid v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid. </eesti>
<inglise>Measures for securing an action filed against the owner of a nominee account, or other restrictions on transfer of the assets of the owner of the nominee account, applied in order to secure proceedings conducted with regard to the owner of the nominee account by a state or local government agency, do not extend to securities of third parties held in the nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Esindajakontol olevatest v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest tulenevate &otilde;iguste teostamiseks on &otilde;igustatud ja kohustuste t&auml;itmise eest vastutav esindajakonto omanik. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The owner of a nominee account is entitled to exercise the rights arising from securities held in the nominee account and is liable for performance of the obligations arising from such securities. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberist tuleneva h&auml;&auml;le&otilde;iguse ja muude &otilde;iguste teostamisel peab esindajakonto omanik j&auml;rgima kliendi korraldusi. </eesti>
<inglise>In the exercise of voting rights and other rights arising from a security, the owner of a nominee account shall follow the orders of the client. </inglise>
<eesti>Kliendi n&otilde;udel peab ta andma kliendile n&otilde;utavas vormis volituse esindajakonto omaniku esindamiseks v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest tulenevate &otilde;iguste teostamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>At the request of the client, the owner of a nominee account shall grant authorisation in the required format to the client in order for the client to represent the owner in the exercise of rights arising from securities. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Esindajakontol ei v&otilde;i hoida pensionifondi osakuid. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Units of pension funds shall not be held in a nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Esindajakonto kohta kantakse registrisse m&auml;rkus, et tegu on esindajakontoga. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A notation shall be made in the register with regard to a nominee account indicating that the account is a nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakonto puhul ei kanta registrisse andmeid isikute kohta, kellele kuuluvad esindajakontol olevad v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid. </eesti>
<inglise>In the case of a nominee account, information regarding the persons who own the securities held in the nominee account shall not be entered in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakonto puhul kantakse registrisse andmed esindajakonto omaniku kohta ja muud k&auml;esoleva seadusega n&otilde;utud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>In the case of a nominee account, information regarding the owner of the nominee account and other information required by this Act shall be entered in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Esindajakonto omanik on kohustatud pidama esindajakontol hoitavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite &uuml;le arvestust. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The owner of a nominee account is required to maintain records on the securities held in the account. </inglise>
<eesti>Arvestuses n&auml;idatakse muu hulgas &auml;ra k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 5 l&otilde;ike 4 punktides 1-4 ja 7-10 toodud andmed k&otilde;ikide isikute kohta, kelle k&auml;sundi kohaselt esindajakonto omanik v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid on omandanud. </eesti>
<inglise>The records shall set out, inter alia, information specified in clauses 5 (4) 1) -4) and 7) -10) of this Act with regard to all persons with whom the owner of the nominee account has entered into an authorisation agreement pursuant to which the owner of the nominee account has acquired securities. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakontosid peetakse eraldi Eesti juriidiliste isikute v&otilde;i muude institutsioonide, Eesti f&uuml;&uuml;siliste isikute, v&auml;lisriikide juriidiliste isikute v&otilde;i muude institutsioonide ja v&auml;lisriikide f&uuml;&uuml;siliste isikute arvel hoitavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>Nominee accounts shall be maintained separately for securities held on behalf of Estonian legal persons or other institutions, Estonian natural persons, foreign legal persons or other institutions, and foreign natural persons. </inglise>
<eesti>Esindajakontol v&otilde;ivad olla mitme eelnimetatud isiku arvel hoitavad v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid. </eesti>
<inglise>Securities held on behalf of several of the aforementioned persons may be held in the same nominee account. </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Esindajakonto omanik on kohustatud klientidega, kelle arvel ta v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid esindajakontol hoiab, s&otilde;lmima kirjaliku lepingu, milles muu hulgas s&auml;testatakse k&auml;sundiandja kohustus Eesti seadusega etten&auml;htud juhtudel ja korras teatada seadusega etten&auml;htud osalusk&uuml;nnise &uuml;letamisest &auml;ri&uuml;hingutes v&otilde;i k&uuml;sida selleks p&auml;deva organi luba. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) The owner of a nominee account is required to enter into written agreements with clients on whose behalf the owner holds securities in the nominee account and such agreements shall, inter alia, provide for the obligation of the mandator to give notice if a holding in a company exceeds the threshold prescribed by law or to obtain the permission of the competent body for the holding to exceed the threshold, in the cases and pursuant to the procedure prescribed by Estonian law. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Esindajakontol olevaid v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid ei loeta avalike osaluspiirangute v&otilde;i muude sarnaste n&otilde;uete hindamisel, samuti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru seadusest tuleneva kohustusliku &uuml;lev&otilde;tmispakkumise tegemise eelduste arvestamisel kuuluvaks esindajakonto omanikule, vaid isikule, kelle arvel v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid hoitakse. </eesti>
<inglise>(9) Upon valuation of public restrictions on holdings or other similar claims and upon assessment of the prerequisites for mandatory takeover bids arising from the Securities Market Act, securities held in a nominee account are not deemed to be owned by the owner of the nominee account but by the person on whose behalf the securities are held. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Registri avalikkus </eesti>
<inglise>Access to register </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 4 punktides 1 ja 2 nimetatud andmetega on &otilde;igus tutvuda ning saada v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid registrist ja &auml;rakirju dokumentidest k&otilde;igil isikutel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) All persons have the right to access information specified in clauses 4 1) and 2) of this Act and to obtain extracts from the register and transcripts of documents. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 4 punktis 3 nimetatud andmetega, v&auml;lja arvatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omaniku aadress, on &otilde;igus tutvuda ja saada v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The following have the right to access information specified in clause 4 3) of this Act, excluding the addresses of the owners of securities, and to obtain extracts: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rsil noteeritud aktsiate kohta - k&otilde;igil isikutel; </eesti>
<inglise>1) information concerning shares quoted on the stock exchange - all persons; </inglise>
<eesti>2) k&auml;esoleva l&otilde;ike punktis 1 nimetamata aktsiate kohta - emitendil ning &auml;riseadustiku (RT I 1995, 26/28, 355; 1998, 91/93, 1500; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355; 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373; 2001, 24, 133; 34, 185; 56, 332; 336) &sect; 234 l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud isikutel; </eesti>
<inglise>2) information concerning shares not specified in clause 1) of this subsection - the issuer and persons specified in subsection 234 (1) of the Commercial Code (RT I 1995, 26/28, 355; 1998, 91/93, 1500; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355; 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373; 2001, 24, 133; 34, 185; 56, 332; 336); </inglise>
<eesti>3) osade kohta - emitendil ning &auml;riseadustiku &sect; 182 l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud isikutel; </eesti>
<inglise>3) information concerning shares in private limited companies - the issuer and persons specified in subsection 182 (2) of the Commercial Code; </inglise>
<eesti>4) k&auml;esoleva l&otilde;ike punktides 1-3 nimetamata v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta - emitendil ja teistel isikutel, kellel on selleks &otilde;igustatud huvi. </eesti>
<inglise>4) information concerning securities not specified in clauses 1) -3) of this subsection - the issuer and other persons with a legitimate interest. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 5 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud andmetega v&otilde;ib tutvuda ja neist v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid saada &uuml;ksnes v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik ja tema poolt selleks volitatud isik. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Only the owner of the securities account and persons authorised thereby for such purpose have the right to access and obtain extracts from the information specified in subsection 5 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Nimetatud andmetega v&otilde;ivad tutvuda ja v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid saada samuti j&auml;rgmised asutused ja isikud, kui nad t&otilde;estavad registripidajale kirjalikult oma &otilde;igustatud huvi olemasolu nende andmetega tutvumise v&otilde;i neist v&auml;ljav&otilde;tete saamise vastu: </eesti>
<inglise>The following bodies and persons may also access and obtain extracts of such information if they prove to the registrar in writing that they have a legitimate interest in accessing such information and obtaining extracts therefrom: </inglise>
<eesti>1) asutused, kes seaduse alusel teostavad riiklikku j&auml;relevalvet; </eesti>
<inglise>1) agencies exercising state supervision pursuant to law; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kohus asja menetlemisel; </eesti>
<inglise>2) courts during proceedings of matters; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kohtut&auml;itur kohtuotsuse t&auml;itmise v&otilde;i hagi tagamise eesm&auml;rgil; </eesti>
<inglise>3) bailiffs, in order to enforce a court judgment or secure an action; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kriminaalasjas eeluurimist teostav asutus; </eesti>
<inglise>4) agencies conducting preliminary investigation in criminal matters; </inglise>
<eesti>5) Maksuamet seoses konkreetse maksuasja menetlemisega; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the Tax Board in connection with proceedings concerning matters pertaining to specific taxes; </inglise>
<eesti>6) oma p&auml;devuse piires j&auml;relevalvet teostav v&auml;&auml;rtpaberib&ouml;rs. </eesti>
<inglise>6) the stock exchange, in the exercise of supervision within the limits of the competence thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;ljav&otilde;tete ja &auml;rakirjade saamine toimub soovija kulul, v&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 3 teises lauses nimetatud juhtudel. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Extracts and transcripts are issued at the expense of the person requesting them, except in the cases specified in the second sentence of subsection (3) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidaja v&otilde;ib kehtestada k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1-3 nimetatud andmete v&auml;ljastamiseks t&auml;psema korra. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The registrar may establish a more detailed procedure for the release of information specified in subsections (1) -(3) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Registri andmetega tutvumine muude kui k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1-3 nimetatud isikute v&otilde;i asutuste poolt ja muul kui seal s&auml;testatud viisil on lubatud &uuml;ksnes seadusega s&auml;testatud ulatuses ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) Access to register information by persons or bodies other than those specified in subsections (1) -(3) of this section and in a manner other than that provided in the same subsections is permitted only to the extent and pursuant to the procedure provided by law. </inglise>
<eesti>3. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 3 </inglise>
<eesti>Registritoimingud </eesti>
<inglise>Register Acts </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>Registreerimise kord </eesti>
<inglise>Registration procedure </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kannete tegemine registrisse, registripidamine ja registriandmete s&auml;ilitamine toimub rahandusministri poolt kehtestatud registripidamise korras (edaspidi registripidamise kord), kui seadusega ei s&auml;testata teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Unless otherwise provided by law, entries are made in the register, the register is maintained and register information is preserved pursuant to the procedure for maintenance of the register, established by the Minister of Finance (hereinafter the procedure for maintenance of the register). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidamise korras etten&auml;htud ulatuses ei pea emitent k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud andmeid esitama, kui need on registripidajale arvutiv&otilde;rgu vahendusel k&auml;ttesaadavad &auml;riregistrist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) To the extent prescribed by the procedure for maintenance of the register, an issuer is not required to submit information provided for in this Act if such information is available to the registrar from the commercial register through a computer network. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>Registreerimise &otilde;iguslikud tagaj&auml;rjed </eesti>
<inglise>Legal consequences of registration </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Otilde;igus registrisse kantud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitele loetakse kolmandate isikute suhtes kehtivaks &uuml;ksnes juhul, kui &otilde;igus on kantud registrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Rights to securities entered in the register are deemed applicable with regard to third parties only if such rights are entered in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui isik omandab registrile tuginedes heauskselt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi v&otilde;i &otilde;iguse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberile, loetakse register tema suhtes &otilde;igeks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If a person acquires a security or a right to a security in good faith relying on the register, the register is deemed correct with regard to the person. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja registreerib v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid emitendi kirjaliku v&otilde;i kirjalikku taasesitamist ja isiku identifitseerimist v&otilde;imaldava taotluse alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall register securities on the basis of an application from the issuer or an application enabling written reproduction and identification of the person. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse vormi kehtestab registripidaja. </eesti>
<inglise>The format of such applications shall be established by the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud taotlusele tuleb lisada j&auml;rgmised dokumendid: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The following documents shall be appended to an application specified in subsection (1) of this section: </inglise>
<eesti>1) registreeritavate v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanike nimekiri (aktsiaraamat, osanike nimekiri vms); </eesti>
<inglise>1) a list of the owners of the securities to be registered (the share register, list of shareholders, etc.) </inglise>
<eesti>2) aktsiate v&otilde;i osade registreerimisel &auml;ri&uuml;hingu &auml;riregistri kaardi t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri v&otilde;i t&otilde;estatud registri v&auml;ljav&otilde;te v&otilde;i registreerimistunnistuse notariaalselt t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri, samuti taotluse esitaja volitusi t&otilde;endavad muud dokumendid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) in the case of registration of shares, a certified transcript of the commercial registry card of the company or a certified extract from the register or a notarised transcript of the registration certificate, and other documents certifying the authority of the person submitting the application; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite avaliku emissiooni registreerimisel Finantsinspektsiooni poolt v&auml;ljastatud emissiooni registreerimistunnistuse t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri, samuti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite emissiooniprospekt v&otilde;i emissioonitingimused; </eesti>
<inglise>3) in the case of registration of a public issue of securities, a certified transcript of the issue registration certificate issued by the Financial Supervision Authority, and the prospectus of the issue or other conditions for the issue; </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>4) makseagendiks oleva emitendi esindaja andmed, kes on volitatud emitendi nimel tegema v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanikele makseid emitendi poolt emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitelt; </eesti>
<inglise>4) information concerning the representative of the issuer acting as a paying agent who is authorised to make payments in the name of the issuer to the owners of securities on securities issued by the issuer; </inglise>
<eesti>5) osade esmakordsel registreerimisel osanike otsus osade registreerimise kohta registris; </eesti>
<inglise>5) upon first registration of shares, the decision of the shareholders to enter the shares in the register; </inglise>
<eesti>6) muud registripidamise korras etten&auml;htud andmed ja dokumendid. </eesti>
<inglise>6) other information and documents prescribed by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidajal on &otilde;igus kehtestada t&auml;iendavaid n&otilde;udeid esitatavatele dokumentidele ja n&otilde;uda lisaks k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1 ja 2 nimetatutele t&auml;iendavate dokumentide esitamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The registrar has the right to establish additional requirements for documents to be submitted and to demand submission of additional documents to supplement those specified in subsections (1) and (2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberid registreeritakse viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul p&auml;rast k&otilde;igi v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimiseks vajalike andmete ja dokumentide esitamist registripidajale. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Securities are registered within five working days after all information and documents necessary for the registration of the securities have been submitted to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamine </eesti>
<inglise>Opening of securities account </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avab registripidaja kontohalduri poolt temale edastatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontot omada sooviva isiku kirjaliku v&otilde;i kirjalikku taasesitamist ja isiku identifitseerimist v&otilde;imaldava taotluse alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall open a securities account on the basis of an application from the person who wishes to own a securities account or an application enabling written reproduction and identification of the person, which is forwarded by the account administrator to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi registreerimisel puudub v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omaniku nimel registris avatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto, avab registripidaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omaniku nimel ajutise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto emitendi taotluse alusel, investeerimisfondi osakute v&otilde;i aktsiate puhul fondivalitseja taotluse alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon registration of securities in the absence of a securities account opened in the register in the name of the owner of the securities, the registrar shall open a temporary securities account in the name of the owner of the securities on the basis of an application from the issuer or, in the case of units or shares in an investment fund, on the basis of an application from the management company. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Kannete tegemine ja parandamine </eesti>
<inglise>Making and correction of entries </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kande aluseks v&otilde;ib olla emitendi taotlus, kontohalduri korraldus, kohtulahend v&otilde;i registripidamise korra v&otilde;i muu &otilde;igusaktiga etten&auml;htud alus. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An entry may be made on the basis of an application from an issuer, an order of an account administrator or a court decision, or on another basis prescribed by the procedure for maintenance of the register or by other legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kannete tegemine toimub vastavalt registripidamise korras s&auml;testatule, kui seadusega ei s&auml;testata teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Entries shall be made pursuant to the provisions of the procedure for maintenance of the register unless otherwise provided by law. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja peab kande parandama j&otilde;ustunud kohtulahendi alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The registrar shall correct an entry on the basis of a court decision which has entered into force. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja v&otilde;ib parandada kande ka enda algatusel, kui ta avastab kandes vea v&otilde;i kande puudumise ja kui kande parandamisega ei kahjustata kellegi &otilde;igusi. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar may correct an entry on its own initiative if the registrar discovers that an entry is incorrect or missing and if correction of the entry does not violate anyone's rights. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidaja peab s&auml;ilitama andmeid k&otilde;igist avastatud kannete vigadest ja kannete puudumisest ning samuti tema tehtud parandustest. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The registrar shall preserve information concerning all incorrect or missing entries discovered and concerning corrections made by the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kande parandamisel teatab registripidaja sellest k&otilde;ikidele isikutele, keda kande muutmine puudutab. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If the registrar corrects an entry, it shall notify all persons concerned of the correction. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Increase of share capital </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kui emitendi aktsiad v&otilde;i osad on registris registreeritud, peab emitent aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamisel t&auml;iendavalt emiteeritud aktsiad v&otilde;i aktsiate v&otilde;i osade nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse suurendamise registris registreerima. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If the shares of an issuer have been entered in the register, the issuer shall enter the shares issued additionally upon an increase in share capital, or any increase in the nominal value of the shares in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Emitent peab aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamise &auml;riregistrisse kandmiseks esitatavale avaldusele lisama registripidaja teatise selle kohta, et emitent on teda teavitanud aktsiate v&otilde;i osade v&auml;ljalaskmisest v&otilde;i nende nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse suurendamisest aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamise ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In order to enter an increase in share capital in the commercial register, the issuer shall, together with an application, submit a notice from the registrar that the issuer has notified the registrar of an issue of shares or of an increase in the nominal value of the shares and of the amount by which the share capital will increase. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamise korral ei v&otilde;i t&auml;iendavalt emiteeritud aktsiatest v&otilde;i osadest v&otilde;i aktsiate v&otilde;i osade nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse suurenemisest tulenevaid &otilde;igusi teostada enne, kui aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamine on kantud &auml;riregistrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the case of an increase in share capital, rights arising from additionally issued shares or from an increase in the nominal value of the shares shall not be exercised before entry of the increase in share capital in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja teeb vastavate aktsiate v&otilde;i osade kohta registrisse m&auml;rke. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall make a notation in the register concerning such shares. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui aktsia v&otilde;i osa omanik v&otilde;&otilde;randab enne aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali suurendamise &auml;riregistrisse kandmist k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud aktsiad v&otilde;i osad, mille kohta on registrisse kantud m&auml;rge, tuleb vastav m&auml;rge kanda ka aktsia v&otilde;i osa omandaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If, before entry of an increase in share capital in the commercial register, the owner of a share transfers shares specified in subsection (3) of this section concerning which a notation has been made in the register, the corresponding notation shall also be made in the securities account of the transferee of the shares. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Reduction of share capital </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kui emitendi aktsiad v&otilde;i osad on registris registreeritud, peab emitent aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamisel aktsiate v&otilde;i osade t&uuml;histamise v&otilde;i aktsiate v&otilde;i osade nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse v&auml;hendamise registris registreerima. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If the shares of an issuer have been entered in the register, the issuer shall enter cancellation of shares upon a reduction of share capital, or any reduction of the nominal value of shares in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Emitent peab aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamise &auml;riregistrisse kandmiseks esitatavale avaldusele lisama registripidaja teatise selle kohta, et emitent on teda teavitanud aktsiate v&otilde;i osade t&uuml;histamisest v&otilde;i nende nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse v&auml;hendamisest aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamise ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In order to enter a reduction of share capital in the commercial register, the issuer shall, together with an application, submit a notice from the registrar that the issuer has notified the registrar of a cancellation of shares or of a reduction of the nominal value of the shares and of the amount by which the share capital will be reduced. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Aktsiate t&uuml;histamisel v&auml;hendatakse aktsion&auml;ri v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol olevate aktsiate, sealhulgas koormatud aktsiate arvu proportsionaalselt. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon a cancellation of shares, the number of shares, including encumbered shares, in the securities account of a shareholder shall be reduced proportionally. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamise korral v&otilde;ib t&uuml;histamisele v&otilde;i nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse v&auml;hendamisele kuuluvatest aktsiatest v&otilde;i osadest tulenevaid &otilde;igusi teostada seni, kuni aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitali v&auml;hendamine on kantud &auml;riregistrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) In the case of a reduction of share capital, rights arising from shares subject to cancellation or from a reduction of nominal value may be exercised until entry of the reduction of share capital in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja teeb t&uuml;histamisele kuuluvate aktsiate v&otilde;i osade kohta registrisse m&auml;rke. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall make a notation in the register concerning shares subject to cancellation. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kui aktsia v&otilde;i osa omanik v&otilde;&otilde;randab k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud aktsiad v&otilde;i osad, mille kohta on registrisse kantud m&auml;rge, enne aktsiakapitali v&auml;hendamise &auml;riregistrisse kandmist, tuleb vastav m&auml;rge kanda ka aktsia v&otilde;i osa omandaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) If, before entry of a reduction of share capital in the commercial register the owner of a share transfers shares specified in subsection (4) of this section concerning which a notation has been made in the register, the corresponding notation shall also be made in the securities account of the transferee of the shares. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 15. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 15. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekanne </eesti>
<inglise>Transfer of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekanne on registrisse kantud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kirjendamine &uuml;helt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontolt teisele registripidaja poolt esimese v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto debiteerimise ning teise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto krediteerimise teel vastava arvu v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&otilde;rra. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A transfer of securities is a transfer of securities entered in the register from one securities account to another by the registrar by way of debiting the first securities account and crediting the other securities account in the amount of the corresponding number of securities. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande v&otilde;ib teha kontohalduri korraldusel v&otilde;i muul registripidamise korras s&auml;testatud alusel, kui seadusega ei ole s&auml;testatud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>A transfer of securities may be performed on the order of an account administrator or on another basis provided for in the procedure for maintenance of the register, unless otherwise provided by law. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekanded, millega kaasnevad rahalised arveldused (v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekanne makse vastu), teeb registripidaja m&auml;&auml;ratud v&auml;&auml;rtusp&auml;eval kas rahaliste kohustuste arveldamisega samaaegselt v&otilde;i p&auml;rast rahaliste kohustuste arveldamist vastavalt registripidamise korrale. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall perform transfers of securities involving cash settlements (transfers of securities against payment) on the specified value date either simultaneously with settling the financial obligations or after settling the financial obligations and pursuant to the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohalduri poolt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande tegemiseks registripidajale antavas korralduses edastamisele kuuluvad andmed ning korralduse edastamise viisi kehtestab registripidaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Information to be submitted in an order issued by an account administrator to the registrar for the performance of a transfer of securities, and the means of submission of the order shall be established by the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja keeldub &uuml;lekandekorralduse t&auml;itmisest, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar shall refuse to execute a transfer order if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) korraldus v&otilde;i selles sisalduvad andmed ei vasta seaduse v&otilde;i registripidamise korraga kehtestatud n&otilde;uetele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the order or the information contained therein does not meet the requirements established by an Act or the procedure for maintenance of the register; </inglise>
<eesti>2) korraldus ei ole tehtud p&auml;deva isiku poolt; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the order is not issued by a competent person; </inglise>
<eesti>3) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol puuduvad tehingu realiseerimiseks vajalikud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the securities necessary for performance of the transaction are not in the securities account; </inglise>
<eesti>4) makse vastu v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande korral puudub rahaliste kohustuste arveldamiseks vajalik raha; </eesti>
<inglise>4) there is no money for the settlement of financial obligations in the case of a transfer of securities against payment; </inglise>
<eesti>5) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi&uuml;lekande tegemiseks edastatud korraldused tehingu m&otilde;lema poole kontohalduritelt erinevad teineteisest. </eesti>
<inglise>5) orders which the account administrators of both parties to the transaction have issued for performance of the transfer of securities differ. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 16. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 16. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite pantimine </eesti>
<inglise>Pledging of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite pantimine registreeritakse registris pantija kontohalduri korraldusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Pledges of securities shall be entered in the register on the order of the account administrator of the pledgor. </inglise>
<eesti>Juhise pandi registreerimise kohta annab v&auml;lja pantija. </eesti>
<inglise>An instruction for the registration of a pledge shall be issued by the pledgor. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberi pant tekib pandi registreerimisest registris. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A pledge of securities is created upon entry of the pledge in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja teeb panditud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole registris m&auml;rke. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall make a notation concerning pledged securities in a securities account in the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Pandi registreerimise korralduses peavad sisalduma j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An order for the registration of a pledge shall contain the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) pantija ja pandipidaja nimi ja aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name and address of the pledgor and the pledgee; </inglise>
<eesti>2) pantija ja pandipidaja isikukood (selle puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg) v&otilde;i v&otilde;imaluse korral registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the personal identification code of the pledgor and the pledgee (in the absence thereof, the date of birth) or, if possible, the registry code; </inglise>
<eesti>3) panditud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi liik, kogus ning emitendi nimi ja asukoht; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the type and amount of the pledged securities and the name and seat of the issuer; </inglise>
<eesti>4) muud registripidamise korras s&auml;testatud andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>4) other information provided by the procedure for the maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Panditud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi k&auml;sutamisel kehtib pant v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omandaja suhtes edasi. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Upon disposal of a pledged security, the pledge is also valid with regard to the transferee of the security. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja kannab pandi &uuml;le panditud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi omandaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontole. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar shall transfer the pledge to the securities account of the transferee of the pledged security. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Korralduse pandi kustutamise kohta annab kontohaldurile pandipidaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) An order for the deletion of a pledge shall be issued to an account administrator by the pledgee. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberi pandiga tagatud n&otilde;ude t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise korral v&otilde;ib panditud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi n&otilde;ude katteks realiseerida kohtut&auml;ituri poolt pantija kontohaldurile antud korralduse alusel, kui pantija ja pandipidaja vahelises kokkuleppes ei ole s&auml;testatud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) Upon failure to satisfy a claim secured by a pledge of securities, the pledged securities may, in order to cover the claim, be transferred on the basis of an order issued to the account administrator of the pledgor by the bailiff, unless otherwise provided by an agreement between the pledgee and the pledgor. </inglise>
<eesti>Pantija ja pandipidaja kokkuleppe alusel v&otilde;ib panditud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite realiseerimisest etteteatamise t&auml;htaeg olla l&uuml;hem asja&otilde;igusseaduse (RT I 1993, 39, 590; 1999, 44, 509) &sect;-s 293 s&auml;testatust. </eesti>
<inglise>On the basis of an agreement between the pledgor and the pledgee, the term for the advance notice to be given of a transfer of pledged securities may be shorter than the term provided by &sect; 293 of the Law of Property Act (RT I 1993, 39, 590; 1999, 44, 509). </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur ega registripidaja ei kontrolli pandi realiseerimiseks &otilde;igusliku aluse olemasolu ega vastuta sellest tuleneva v&otilde;imaliku kahju eest. </eesti>
<inglise>The account administrator and the registrar do not verify the existence of a legal basis for the transfer of pledged securities and are not liable for any potential damage arising from the transfer. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 17. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 17. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite blokeerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Freezing of securities </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto blokeerimine on v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto k&auml;sutamist ajutiselt piirava kirje kandmine registrisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The freezing of securities or a securities account is the making of a register entry concerning a temporary restriction on the disposal of the securities or the securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberid v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&otilde;ib blokeerida registritoimingu tegemise tagamiseks, &otilde;igusaktidega etten&auml;htud juhtudel ja korras ka sissen&otilde;ude p&ouml;&ouml;ramiseks ning hagi tagamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>Securities or a securities account may be frozen in order to secure the performance of a register act and, in the cases and pursuant to the procedure provided by legislation, to make a claim for payment or to secure an action. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja blokeerib v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto j&auml;rgmistel alustel: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall freeze securities or a securities account on the following grounds: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kohtuotsus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a court judgment; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kohtu v&otilde;i uurimisorgani m&auml;&auml;rus; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a court ruling or an order of an investigative body; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kohtut&auml;ituri korraldus; </eesti>
<inglise>3) an order of a bailiff; </inglise>
<eesti>4) muu &otilde;igusaktidega etten&auml;htud alus. </eesti>
<inglise>4) other grounds prescribed by legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberid v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto j&auml;&auml;vad blokeerituks kuni vastava registritoimingu tegemiseni, blokeerimise aluseks oleva korralduse t&uuml;histamiseni, uue korralduse tegemiseni v&otilde;i muu &otilde;igusaktides etten&auml;htud ajani. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Securities or a securities account remain frozen until a corresponding register entry is made, the order on the basis of which the securities were frozen is cancelled or a new order is issued, or until another time prescribed by legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 18. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 18. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kustutamine registrist </eesti>
<inglise>Deletion of securities from register </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Emitendi l&otilde;ppemise korral kustutatakse registrist k&otilde;ik emitendi poolt emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If an issuer is dissolved, all securities issued by the issuer shall be deleted from the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registris registreeritud Eesti &auml;ri&uuml;hingu osad v&otilde;i aktsiad kustutatakse registrist &uuml;ksnes vastava &auml;ri&uuml;hingu l&otilde;ppemisel likvideerimis- v&otilde;i pankrotimenetluse l&otilde;petamisega, samuti &auml;ri&uuml;hingu &uuml;hinemise, jagunemise v&otilde;i &uuml;mberkujundamise korral. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The shares of an Estonian company entered in the register shall be deleted from the register only upon dissolution of the company, after the termination of the liquidation or bankruptcy proceedings, or upon the merger, division or transformation of the company. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&otilde;lakohustused kustutatakse registrist p&auml;rast nende lunastamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Debt obligations shall be deleted from the register after their redemption. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui registris registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto sisaldab v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid, mis on eeldatavalt kaotanud oma kehtivuse v&otilde;i mille registreerimisest on m&ouml;&ouml;dunud &uuml;le 20 aasta ja mis on suure t&otilde;en&auml;osusega l&otilde;ppenud v&otilde;i millel suure t&otilde;en&auml;osusega puudub omanik, avaldab registripidaja ametlikus v&auml;ljaandes Ametlikud Teadaanded ja v&auml;hemalt &uuml;hes &uuml;leriigilise levikuga p&auml;evalehes &uuml;leskutse sellele v&auml;&auml;rtpaberile pretendeerivatele isikutele oma &otilde;igustest teatada kolme kuu jooksul, arvates &uuml;leskutse avaldamisest ametlikus v&auml;ljaandes Ametlikud Teadaanded. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If a securities account entered in the register includes securities which are presumed to have become invalid or which were registered more than twenty years ago and have most probably been terminated or most probably do not have an owner, the registrar shall publish an invitation in the official publication Ametlikud Teadaanded (2) and at least one national daily newspaper for persons claiming the rights to such securities to give notice of their rights within three months as of the publication of the invitation in the official publication Ametlikud Teadaanded. </inglise>
<eesti>Registrisse omanikena kantud isikuid tuleb teavitada eraldi t&auml;htkirjaga. </eesti>
<inglise>Persons who are entered in the register as owners shall be notified by a separate registered letter. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui t&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumisel ei ole keegi registripidajale endast teatanud, kustutab registripidaja sellise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberi. </eesti>
<inglise>If no one has addressed the registrar by the end of the term, the registrar shall delete the corresponding securities. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 19. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 19. </inglise>
<eesti>Emitendi teavitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Giving notification to issuer </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja edastab emitendi n&otilde;udel v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte registrist emitendi poolt emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite kohta kolme t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul vastavalt registripidamise korras s&auml;testatule. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) At the request of an issuer, the registrar shall, within three working days and pursuant to the provisions of the procedure for maintenance of the register, provide an extract from the register concerning securities issued by the issuer. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud v&auml;ljav&otilde;ttes peavad sisalduma: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An extract specified in subsection (1) of this section shall include: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanike nimed; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the names of the owners of the securities; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanike isiku- v&otilde;i registrikoodid (isikukoodi puudumisel s&uuml;nniaeg) ja aadressid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the personal identification codes or registry codes (or, in the absence of a personal identification code, the date of birth) and addresses of the owners of the securities; </inglise>
<eesti>3) teave v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanike v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodel olevate emitendi poolt emiteeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite nimiv&auml;&auml;rtuse ja arvu kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>3) information concerning the nominal value and amount of securities issued by the issuer which are in the securities accounts of owners of securities. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 20. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 20. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku teavitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Notification of owners of securities accounts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja edastab v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikule teatise v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avamise kohta, kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik ei ole kirjalikult sellest &otilde;igusest loobunud. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall send a notice concerning the opening of a securities account to the owner of the account unless the owner has waived such right in writing. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja peab tagama registritoiminguid iseloomustavate andmete avaldamise vastavalt registripidamise korras s&auml;testatule. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall ensure disclosure of information concerning register acts pursuant to the provisions of the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmed loetakse avaldatuks hetkest, mil on toimunud nende salvestamine &uuml;ldsusele avatud arvutis&uuml;steemi. </eesti>
<inglise>Information is deemed to be disclosed as of its recording in a computer system accessible to the public. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja peab v&otilde;imaldama k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud andmetega tutvuda hiljemalt viiendaks t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;evaks emitendilt vastava teabe saamisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The registrar shall provide access to information specified in subsection (2) of this section by the fifth working day as of receipt of the corresponding information from the issuer at the latest. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja edastab igale v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikule, kelle v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol on v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid, v&auml;hemalt &uuml;ks kord kalendriaasta jooksul hiljemalt 31. jaanuariks teatise, milles on &auml;ra n&auml;idatud selle isiku v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite j&auml;&auml;k eelmise kalendriaasta viimase p&auml;eva seisuga, kui v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik ei ole kirjalikult sellest &otilde;igusest loobunud. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The registrar shall, at least once per calendar year and not later than by 31 January, send a notice to each owner of a securities account whose securities account includes securities, setting out the balance of the securities registered in the securities account of the person as on the last day of the previous calendar year, unless the owner of the securities account has waived such right in writing. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidaja edastab v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikule viimase poolt m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimustel v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol tehtud registritoimingute kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The registrar shall, under the conditions specified by the owner of a securities account, send a statement of the securities account concerning register entries made in the securities account to the owner of the securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1, 4 ja 5 nimetatud dokumentide vorm ja v&auml;ljastamise t&auml;psem kord m&auml;&auml;ratakse registripidamise korraga. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The standard formats of the documents specified in subsections (1), (4) and (5) of this section and the detailed procedure for the issue of the documents shall be established by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) V&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikul on &otilde;igus n&otilde;uda kontohaldurilt igal pangap&auml;eval teavet tema v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite ning v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol tehtud registritoimingute kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The owner of a securities account has the right to request the account administrator to submit information on each banking day concerning the securities registered in the securities account and the register entries made with regard to the securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 21. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 21. </inglise>
<eesti>Andmete esitamine registripidajale </eesti>
<inglise>Submission of information to registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidajal on &otilde;igus tasuta saada registritoimingute tegemiseks teavet ja vajalikke andmeid v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanikelt, emitentidelt, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselistelt osalistelt, fondivalitsejatelt, &auml;riregistri pidajalt ning riigi ja kohaliku omavalitsuse andmekogude vastutavatelt ja volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejatelt. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order for register entries to be made, the registrar has the right to obtain information and necessary data free of charge from the owners of securities accounts, issuers, professional securities market participants, management companies, the registrar of the commercial register and the chief processors and authorised processors of state and local government databases. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Emitent on kohustatud teavitama registripidajat viivitamata: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An issuer is required to notify the registrar promptly of: </inglise>
<eesti>1) k&otilde;igist muudatustest registris registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite omanike &otilde;igustes ja kohustustes, sealhulgas k&otilde;igist muudatustest v&otilde;lakohustuste intressim&auml;&auml;ras v&otilde;i tingimustes ning nende aktsiatega kaasnevates &otilde;igustes, mille vastu vahetusv&otilde;lakirjad on vahetatavad; </eesti>
<inglise>1) all changes in the rights and obligations of the owners of securities entered in the register, including all changes in the interest rates or conditions of debt obligations and in rights arising from shares to which convertible bonds can be converted; </inglise>
<eesti>2) dividendi maksmise kohta otsuse tegemisest; </eesti>
<inglise>2) resolutions concerning the payment of dividends; </inglise>
<eesti>3) emitendi likvideerimisotsuse vastuv&otilde;tmisest v&otilde;i pankrotimenetluse algatamisest emitendi suhtes; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the adoption of a liquidation resolution by the issuer or initiation of bankruptcy proceedings with regard to the issuer; </inglise>
<eesti>4) k&otilde;igist muudatustest emitenti registripidaja suhtes esindama &otilde;igustatud isikute seas; </eesti>
<inglise>4) all alterations among the persons who are entitled to represent the issuer with regard to the registrar; </inglise>
<eesti>5) muudest olulistest asjaoludest. </eesti>
<inglise>5) other significant circumstances. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Igas otsuses, mis on aluseks v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest tulenevate &otilde;iguste tekkimisele, muutmisele v&otilde;i l&otilde;petamisele, peab emitent m&auml;&auml;rama p&auml;eva (fikseerimisp&auml;ev), mis v&otilde;etakse aluseks nende isikute kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisel, kelle &otilde;igusi nimetatud otsus puudutab. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In each resolution on the basis of which rights arising from securities are created, changed or terminated, the issuer shall designate the date (the fixed day) on the basis of which the persons whose rights the resolution concerns are determined. </inglise>
<eesti>Kannete tegemise taotlus ja kannete tegemiseks vajalikud andmed, mille alusel registripidaja teeb emitendi otsusest tulenevad registritoimingud, tuleb esitada registripidajale hiljemalt viis t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva enne fikseerimisp&auml;eva, kui seadusega ei s&auml;testata teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>Applications for register entries to be made, and the information necessary for the entries to be made, on the basis of which the registrar performs the register acts resulting from the resolutions of an issuer, shall be submitted to the registrar not later than five working days before the fixed day, unless otherwise provided by law. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 22. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 22. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja t&ouml;&ouml;keel </eesti>
<inglise>Working language of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidajale esitatavad ja kannete aluseks olevad dokumendid ja registrist v&auml;ljastatavad dokumendid, v&auml;lja arvatud emissioonitingimused ja emissiooniprospekt, peavad olema eesti keeles. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Documents which are submitted to the registrar and on the basis of which register entries are made, and documents issued from the register, except issue conditions and prospectuses, shall be in Estonian. </inglise>
<eesti>Kande aluseks v&otilde;ib olla dokument, mis ei ole eestikeelne, kui registripidaja ja dokumendi esitaja on selles eelnevalt kokku leppinud. </eesti>
<inglise>An entry may be based on a document which is not in Estonian if the registrar and the person submitting the document agree beforehand. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui registripidaja ja dokumendi esitaja ei ole eelnevalt teisiti kokku leppinud, esitatakse v&otilde;&otilde;rkeelne dokument koos t&otilde;estatud eestikeelse t&otilde;lkega. </eesti>
<inglise>Unless otherwise previously agreed by the registrar and the person submitting a document in a foreign language, the document shall be submitted together with a certified translation into Estonian. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidajal on &otilde;igus v&auml;ljastada dokumente ja muid andmeid muus keeles kokkuleppel isikuga, kellele dokumendid v&otilde;i andmed v&auml;ljastatakse. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar has the right to issue documents and other information in other languages if this is agreed upon with the person to whom the documents or information are issued. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 23. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 23. </inglise>
<eesti>Registritoimingute finantseerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Financing of register entries </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja katab oma teenuste osutamise kulud teenuste eest v&otilde;etava tasuga vastavalt registripidaja poolt kinnitatud hinnakirjale. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall cover the costs of the provision of services by charging fees for the services according to the price list approved by the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>Hinnakiri ja selles tehtavad muudatused peavad eelnevalt olema koosk&otilde;lastatud rahandusministriga. </eesti>
<inglise>The price list and any amendments thereto shall be approved beforehand by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja ei v&otilde;ta tasu kohtulahendi v&otilde;i uurimisorgani m&auml;&auml;ruse alusel tehtud kannete v&otilde;i v&auml;ljav&otilde;tete eest ning k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 7 l&otilde;ike 3 teises lauses nimetatud juhtudel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall not charge a fee for entries or extracts made on the basis of a court decision or an order of an investigative body, or in the cases specified in the second sentence of subsection 7 (3) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registris aktsiate registreerimise v&otilde;i registripidaja poolt seoses aktsiate registreerimisega osutatavate teenuste tasude maksmise eest vastutavad aktsiaseltsist emitendi juhatuse liikmed solidaarselt emitendiga. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An issuer which is a public limited company and the members of the management board of the issuer shall be solidarily liable for the payment of fees for the entry of shares in the register or for services provided by the registrar in connection with the registration of shares. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui tasu maksmisega viivitatakse &uuml;le kuue kuu, v&otilde;ib registripidaja taotleda kohtus emitendi sundl&otilde;petamist. </eesti>
<inglise>If the payment of a fee is delayed for more than six months, the registrar may apply for the compulsory dissolution of the issuer in court. </inglise>
<eesti>4. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 4 </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja </eesti>
<inglise>Registrar </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja </eesti>
<inglise>Registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidajaks on aktsiaselts, kellele on see &otilde;igus antud k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar is a public limited company to which the right to act as the registrar has been granted on the basis of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja v&otilde;ib lisaks registripidamisele tegutseda &uuml;ksnes Finantsinspektsiooni lubatud tegevusaladel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In addition to maintenance of the register, the registrar may operate only in areas of activity permitted by the Financial Supervision Authority. </inglise>
<eesti>Loa taotlemise ja l&auml;bivaatamise korra kehtestab rahandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The procedure for requesting and reviewing permission shall be established by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>Finantsinspektsioon keeldub loa andmisest, kui vastav tegevus v&otilde;ib kahjustada registripidamist v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru korrap&auml;rast ja usaldusv&auml;&auml;rset toimimist. </eesti>
<inglise>The Financial Supervision Authority shall refuse to grant permission if the corresponding activity may adversely affect the maintenance of the register or the regular and reliable functioning of the securities market. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja jagunemine ja &uuml;mberkujundamine on keelatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Division and transformation of the registrar is prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja &uuml;hinemiseks on vajalik Finantsinspektsiooni eelnev luba. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Prior permission for the merger of the registrar is required from the Financial Supervision Authority. </inglise>
<eesti>Loa taotlemise ja l&auml;bivaatamise korra kehtestab rahandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The procedure for requesting and reviewing permission shall be established by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>Finantsinspektsioon keeldub loa andmisest, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>The Financial Supervision Authority shall refuse to grant permission if: </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>1) registripidaja v&otilde;i selle aktsion&auml;rid ei vasta &uuml;hinemisel k&auml;esoleva seaduse v&otilde;i selle alusel kehtestatud n&otilde;uetele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) upon merger, the registrar or the shareholders thereof do not meet the requirements of this Act or requirements established on the basis thereof; </inglise>
<eesti>2) registrisse kantud andmete s&auml;ilimine, registritoimingute tegemine v&otilde;i registripidamine ei ole &uuml;hinemisel vajalikul tasemel tagatud; </eesti>
<inglise>2) upon merger, the preservation of register information, performance of register acts or the maintenance of the register is not guaranteed to the extent required; </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;hinemine kahjustab registripidaja v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru korrap&auml;rast ja usaldusv&auml;&auml;rset toimimist. </eesti>
<inglise>3) the merger would adversely affect the regular and reliable functioning of the registrar or the securities market. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja m&auml;&auml;ramine </eesti>
<inglise>Appointment of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja m&auml;&auml;ramise otsustab Vabariigi Valitsus rahandusministri ettepanekul. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Government of the Republic shall decide on the appointment of the registrar on the proposal of the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>Rahandusminister s&otilde;lmib lepingu registripidamiseks Vabariigi Valitsuse m&auml;&auml;ratud registripidajaga. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of Finance shall enter into an agreement for the maintenance of the register with the registrar appointed by the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja valimise t&auml;psema korra ja registripidamiseks s&otilde;lmitava lepingu tingimused kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus. </eesti>
<inglise>The detailed procedure for the election of the registrar, and the conditions of the agreement to be entered into for the maintenance of the register shall be established by the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitav leping registripidamiseks ei v&otilde;i olla pikema t&auml;htajaga kui 20 aastat. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The term of an agreement entered into with the registrar for the maintenance of the register shall not exceed twenty years. </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigil on &otilde;igus registripidamiseks s&otilde;lmitud leping ennet&auml;htaegselt l&otilde;petada m&otilde;juval p&otilde;hjusel, milleks on eelk&otilde;ige registripidajapoolne kohustuste oluline rikkumine v&otilde;i tema maksej&otilde;ulisuse oluline v&auml;henemine. </eesti>
<inglise>The Republic of Estonia has the right to terminate an agreement for the maintenance of the register prematurely if there is good reason therefor, this being primarily material violation of obligations by the registrar or a material decline in the solvency thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Lepingu l&otilde;ppemise v&otilde;i ennet&auml;htaegse l&otilde;petamise korral otsustab Vabariigi Valitsus rahandusministri ettepanekul lepingu pikendamise, uue registripidaja m&auml;&auml;ramise v&otilde;i registripidamise &uuml;leandmise vastavale asutusele. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon expiry or premature termination of an agreement, the Government of the Republic shall, on the proposal of the Minister of Finance, decide to extend the agreement, appoint a new registrar, or transfer the maintenance of the register to an appropriate agency. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 26. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 26. </inglise>
<eesti>N&otilde;uded registripidaja kapitalile </eesti>
<inglise>Requirements for capital of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja aktsiakapital peab olema v&auml;hemalt 3 000 000 krooni ja omakapital v&auml;hemalt 5 000 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The share capital of the registrar shall be at least 3 000 000 kroons and the shareholders' equity at least 5 000 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja reservkapital peab olema v&auml;hemalt 1/5 registripidaja aktsiakapitalist, kuid mitte v&auml;iksem kui registripidaja kuue kuu tegevuskulud. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The legal reserve of the registrar shall be at least one-fifth of the share capital of the registrar but not less than its six months' operating expenses. </inglise>
<eesti>Tegevuskulude arvestamise alused kehtestab rahandusminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The bases for the calculation of operating expenses shall be established by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja aktsiakapitali v&auml;hendamiseks, p&otilde;hikirja muutmiseks ja registripidaja l&otilde;petamiseks on vajalik Finantsinspektsiooni n&otilde;usolek. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The consent of the Financial Supervision Authority is necessary for any reduction of the share capital, amendment of the articles of association, or dissolution of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 27. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 27. </inglise>
<eesti>N&otilde;uded registripidaja aktsiatele </eesti>
<inglise>Requirements for shares of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidajal v&otilde;ivad olla &uuml;ksnes nimelised aktsiad. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar may have only registered shares. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja ei v&otilde;i otseselt ega kaudselt omada v&otilde;i omandada oma aktsiaid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall neither directly nor indirectly own or acquire its own shares. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja aktsiate koormamine ei ole lubatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Encumbrance of the shares of the registrar is prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 28. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 28. </inglise>
<eesti>Osalus registripidajas </eesti>
<inglise>Holdings in registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Oluliseks osaluseks k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses loetakse sellist osalust &auml;ri&uuml;hingus, mis moodustab &auml;ri&uuml;hingu aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitalist v&otilde;i h&auml;&auml;lte arvust 10 protsenti v&otilde;i rohkem. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, a holding in a company which represents 10 per cent or more of the share capital or votes in the company is deemed to be a qualifying holding. </inglise>
<eesti>H&auml;&auml;lte arvestamisel osaluste omandamisel v&otilde;i omamisel l&auml;htutakse krediidiasutuste seaduse (RT I 1999, 23, 349; 2000, 35, 222; 40, 250) &sect;-s 10 s&auml;testatust. </eesti>
<inglise>For the purposes of acquisition or owning of holdings, votes shall be calculated pursuant to the provisions of &sect; 10 of the Credit Institutions Act (RT I 1999, 23, 349; 2000, 35, 222; 40, 250). </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Olulist osalust registripidajas v&otilde;ib omada &uuml;ksnes krediidiasutus, v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutseline osaline, fondivalitseja v&otilde;i kindlustusselts, samuti muu isik, kui viimasel on olulise osaluse omamiseks Finantsinspektsiooni eelnev luba. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Qualifying holdings in the registrar may be owned only by credit institutions, professional securities market participants, management companies, insurance companies, and any other persons who have received prior permission from the Financial Supervision Authority to own a qualifying holding. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui isik kavatseb omandada registripidajas suuremat osalust kui 1/5, 1/3 v&otilde;i 1/2, samuti juhul, kui ta muutub tehingu tagaj&auml;rjel registripidaja emaettev&otilde;tjaks, peab ta selleks taotlema Finantsinspektsioonilt vastava loa. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If a person intends to acquire a holding in the registrar which exceeds one-fifth, one-third or one-half or if the person is to become the parent undertaking of the registrar as a result of the transaction, the person shall request corresponding permission from the Financial Supervision Authority. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) &Uuml;kski krediidiasutus, investeerimis&uuml;hing, fondivalitseja v&otilde;i kindlustusselts ei v&otilde;i otseselt v&otilde;i kaudselt omada registripidajas h&auml;&auml;leenamust v&otilde;i lepingu alusel v&otilde;i ilma selleta valitsevat m&otilde;ju. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) No credit institution, investment firm, management company or insurance company shall directly or indirectly have a majority of the voting rights in or, whether on the basis of an agreement or not, dominant influence over the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.24.05.2001 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 24.05.2001 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 2 ja 3 nimetatud loa taotlemise ja l&auml;bivaatamise korra kehtestab Finantsinspektsioon. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The procedure for requesting and reviewing the permission specified in subsections (2) and (3) of this section shall be established by the Financial Supervision Authority. </inglise>
<eesti>Finantsinspektsioon keeldub loa andmisest, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>The Financial Supervision Authority shall refuse to grant permission if: </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>1) taotleja ei ole t&auml;htaegselt esitanud &otilde;igusaktidega etten&auml;htud andmeid v&otilde;i dokumente v&otilde;i esitatud andmed on eksitavad v&otilde;i ei vasta tegelikkusele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the person requesting the permission fails to submit information or documents prescribed by legislation on time or if the information submitted is misleading or inaccurate; </inglise>
<eesti>2) taotleja tegevus, &auml;risidemed ja omanike struktuur ei ole piisavalt l&auml;bipaistvad; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the activities, business connections and structure of owners of the person requesting the permission are not sufficiently transparent; </inglise>
<eesti>3) taotleja v&otilde;i tema juhtkonna liikmete &auml;rialane reputatsioon ei ole laitmatu; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the business reputation of the person requesting the permission or that of the members of its management board is not impeccable; </inglise>
<eesti>4) taotleja ei ole oma finantsseisundi v&otilde;i &auml;risidemete t&otilde;ttu v&otilde;i muul p&otilde;hjusel v&otilde;imeline tagama registripidaja kindlat ja usaldusv&auml;&auml;rset toimimist; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the person requesting the permission is unable to ensure the sound and reliable functioning of the registrar due to the financial situation or business connections of the person or for any other reason; </inglise>
<eesti>5) osaluse omandamine on vastuolus k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatuga; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the acquisition of a holding is in conflict with the provisions of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>6) osaluse omandamine taotleja poolt v&otilde;ib muul p&otilde;hjusel kahjustada registripidaja v&otilde;i v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru korrap&auml;rast ja usaldusv&auml;&auml;rset toimimist. </eesti>
<inglise>6) the acquisition of a holding by the person requesting the permission may adversely affect the regular and reliable functioning of the registrar or the securities market for any other reason. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kui k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 5 punktides 1-6 nimetatud asjaolud ilmnevad p&auml;rast loa andmist, v&otilde;ib Finantsinspektsioon antud loa t&uuml;histada. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If circumstances specified in clauses (5) 1) -6) of this section become evident after permission has been granted, the Financial Supervision Authority may revoke the permission. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Kui k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 2 ja 3 nimetatud osalus on omandatud ilma Finantsinspektsiooni loata v&otilde;i see luba on t&uuml;histatud, ei omanda tehingu teinud isik omandatud aktsiatega kaasnevat h&auml;&auml;le&otilde;igust ning neid aktsiaid ei arvata &uuml;ldkoosoleku kvoorumisse. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) If a holding specified in subsections (2) or (3) of this section is acquired without the permission of the Financial Supervision Authority or if such permission has been revoked, the person who concluded the transaction shall not acquire the voting rights determined by the acquired shares and the shares shall not be included in the quorum of the general meeting. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui need h&auml;&auml;led siiski arvati &uuml;ldkoosoleku kvoorumisse ja see m&otilde;jutas &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmist, v&otilde;ib kohus Finantsinspektsiooni avalduse alusel tunnistada &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse kehtetuks, kui avaldus on esitatud kolme kuu jooksul &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>If such voting rights are nevertheless included in the quorum of the general meeting and influence the adoption of a resolution of the general meeting, a court may, on the basis of a petition of the Financial Supervision Authority, declare the resolution of the general meeting invalid if the petition is submitted within three months as of the adoption of the resolution of the general meeting. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(8) K&auml;esolevas paragrahvis registripidaja ja selle aktsion&auml;ride suhtes s&auml;testatut kohaldatakse ka registripidaja emaettev&otilde;tja ja selle aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i osanike suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) The provisions of this section concerning the registrar and the shareholders thereof also apply to the parent undertaking of the registrar and the shareholders of the parent undertaking. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 29. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 29. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu ja juhatus </eesti>
<inglise>Supervisory board and management board of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja juhatuses on v&auml;hemalt kaks liiget. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The management board of the registrar shall consist of at least two members. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja p&otilde;hikirjas peab olema ette n&auml;htud n&otilde;ukogu ja juhatuse t&auml;psem t&ouml;&ouml;korraldus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The articles of association of the registrar shall prescribe the organisation of the work of the supervisory board and management board in detail. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu ja juhatuse liikmeks v&otilde;ib olla isik, kellel on oma &uuml;lesannete t&auml;itmiseks vajalik haridus, kogemused, kutsealane sobivus ning laitmatu &auml;rialane reputatsioon. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Persons who have the education, experience and professional qualifications necessary to perform their duties and who have an impeccable business reputation may be members of the supervisory board or management board of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu ja juhatuse liikmete valimiseks v&otilde;i m&auml;&auml;ramiseks on vajalik isiku kirjalik n&otilde;usolek. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) In order to elect or appoint a member of the supervisory board or management board of the registrar, the written consent of the person to be elected or appointed is necessary. </inglise>
<eesti>Koos n&otilde;usolekuga esitab isik &uuml;levaate oma hariduse, t&ouml;&ouml;kogemuse, ettev&otilde;tluses osalemise, karistatuse ja tema kohta karistusregistrisse kantud karistuste kohta ning kinnituse, et talle ei ole teada asjaolud, mis v&auml;listaksid tema &otilde;iguse olla registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;i juhatuse liige. </eesti>
<inglise>A person shall submit his or her consent together with an overview of his or her education, work experience, engagement in enterprise, criminal record and punishments entered in the punishment register, and confirmation that he or she is not aware of any circumstances which preclude his or her right to be a member of the supervisory board or management board of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu ja juhatuse liikmed ning registripidaja t&ouml;&ouml;tajad peavad hoidma registris sisalduvat teavet, mis pole avalikult k&auml;ttesaadav, saladuses nii ametikohustuste t&auml;itmise ajal kui ka p&auml;rast ametikohustuste t&auml;itmise l&otilde;ppemist. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The confidentiality of register information which is not publicly available shall be maintained by the members of the supervisory board and management board of the registrar and the employees of the registrar during the performance of their duties and after they have ceased to perform such duties. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Registripidaja on kohustatud kindlustama registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu ja juhatuse liikmete ning t&ouml;&ouml;tajate ameti- ja t&ouml;&ouml;alastest tegudest tuleneva tsiviilvastutuse. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The registrar is required to insure the professional liability arising from the professional activities of members of the supervisory board and management board and employees of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 30. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 30. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja kohustused registriandmete kaitsmisel ja s&auml;ilitamisel </eesti>
<inglise>Obligations of registrar in protection and preservation of register information </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja peab tagama, et registriandmed oleksid halduslike, f&uuml;&uuml;siliste ning tark- ja riistvaraliste meetmetega asjakohaselt kaitstud loata t&ouml;&ouml;tluse, sealhulgas kasutamise, h&auml;vitamise ning muutmise eest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall ensure that, by means of appropriate administrative and technical measures and measures involving software and hardware, register information is protected against unauthorised processing, including use, destruction or alteration of register information. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja on kohustatud s&auml;ilitama temale kande tegemiseks esitatud andmeid ja dokumente v&auml;hemalt k&uuml;mne aasta v&auml;ltel vastava kande tegemisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Information and documents submitted to the registrar for an entry to be made shall be preserved by the registrar for at least ten years as of the corresponding entry. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esolevas l&otilde;ikes nimetatud andmeid ja dokumente s&auml;ilitatakse dokumentaalselt v&otilde;i dokumentaalset taasesitamist v&otilde;imaldaval viisil. </eesti>
<inglise>Information and documents specified in this subsection shall be preserved as documents or in a form enabling reproduction as documents. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registriandmete arhiveerimine toimub vastavalt registripidamise korras s&auml;testatule. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Register information shall be archived pursuant to the provisions of the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>5. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 5 </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur </eesti>
<inglise>Account Administrator </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 31. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 31. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur </eesti>
<inglise>Account Administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registri kontohaldur on isik, kes edastab registripidajale v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanike korraldusi registritoimingute tegemiseks ning vahendab registripidaja poolt osutatavaid teenuseid k&auml;esoleva seaduse, sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide ning registripidaja ja kontohalduri vahelise lepingu alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An account administrator of the register is a person who communicates the orders of owners of securities accounts to the registrar for the performance of register acts and who, on the basis of this Act, legislation arising therefrom and an agreement between the registrar and the account administrator, mediates the services provided by the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohaldur peab tagama registritoimingute tegemiseks vajalike andmete &otilde;igeaegse edastamise registripidajale ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodega seotud toimingute tegemise oma p&auml;devuse piires koosk&otilde;las k&auml;esoleva seadusega ja registripidamise korras kehtestatud n&otilde;uetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An account administrator shall ensure that information necessary for the performance of register acts is communicated to the registrar on time and that the account administrator performs acts related to securities accounts within the competence thereof and in compliance with this Act and the requirements established by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohaldur tagab, et tema poolt k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel registripidajale edastatavad andmed ja seoses v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontoga salvestatavad andmed oleksid halduslike, f&uuml;&uuml;siliste, tark- ja riistvaraliste meetmetega kaitstud loata t&ouml;&ouml;tluse, sealhulgas kasutamise, h&auml;vitamise ning muutmise eest. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An account administrator shall ensure that, by means of appropriate administrative and technical measures and measures involving software and hardware, information communicated to the registrar by the account administrator on the basis of this Act and information recorded with regard to securities accounts is protected against unauthorised processing, including use, destruction or alteration of such information. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kontohaldur peab vahendama v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikele k&otilde;iki registripidaja pakutavaid teenuseid, kui kontohalduri ja registripidaja vahelise lepinguga ei ole ette n&auml;htud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) An account administrator shall mediate all services provided by the registrar to owners of securities accounts unless otherwise prescribed by an agreement between the account administrator and the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui m&otilde;ne teenuse osutamine on tehnilistel p&otilde;hjustel raskendatud v&otilde;i v&otilde;imatu, peab kontohaldur registripidajat sellest viivitamata teavitama. </eesti>
<inglise>If the provision of a service is made complicated or impossible for technical reasons, the account administrator shall immediately notify the registrar thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kontohalduril on &otilde;igus v&auml;ljastada registrisse kantud andmeid &uuml;ksnes &otilde;igusaktides etten&auml;htud juhtudel ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) An account administrator has the right to release register information only in the cases and pursuant to the procedure prescribed by legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri t&ouml;&ouml;tajad ja juhtorganite liikmed on nii kontohalduri teenistuses olles kui ka p&auml;rast seda kohustatud hoidma t&auml;htajatult saladuses k&otilde;iki registriesemeks olevaid andmeid, mis on neile teatavaks saanud kontohalduri teenistuses olles. </eesti>
<inglise>The employees and members of the management bodies of an account administrator are, while employed by the account administrator and also thereafter, required to maintain indefinitely the confidentiality of all information which is the object of the register and has become known to them while employed by the account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse andmine </eesti>
<inglise>Granting status of account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduriks v&otilde;ivad olla Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselised osalised ja Eesti Pank. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Professional participants in the Estonian securities market and the Bank of Estonia may be account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Lisaks k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud isikutele v&otilde;ib kontohalduriks olla Euroopa Liidu liikmesriigis registreeritud &auml;ri&uuml;hing, millele on antud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegevusluba, samuti &auml;ri&uuml;hing, mis on registreeritud riigis, mis ei ole Euroopa Liidu liikmesriik, kuid millega Eesti Vabariigil on j&otilde;ustunud vastastikuse &otilde;igusabi osutamise leping, ning millele on antud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalise tegevusluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In addition to the persons specified in subsection (1) of this section, companies holding the activity licence of a professional securities market participant and registered in a Member State of the European Union, and companies holding the activity licence of a professional securities market participant and registered in a country which is not a Member State of the European Union but with which the Republic of Estonia has an agreement of mutual legal assistance which has entered into force may also be account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohalduri staatuse andmise k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1 ja 2 nimetatud isikutele otsustab registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The supervisory board of the registrar shall decide whether to grant the status of an account administrator to a person specified in subsection (1) or (2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidajal on &otilde;igus n&otilde;uda kontohaldurilt v&otilde;i kontohalduri staatuse taotlejalt teavet registripidamise korras kehtestatud ulatuses eesm&auml;rgiga hinnata nende vastavust kontohaldurile seadusega ja registripidamise korraga esitatavatele n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar has the right to request an account administrator or an applicant for the status of an account administrator to submit information to the extent established by the procedure for maintenance of the register in order to assess their compliance with the requirements prescribed for account administrators by law and the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>N&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;ib keelduda kontohalduri staatuse andmisest &uuml;ksnes p&otilde;hjusel, et kontohaldur ei vasta talle kehtestatud n&otilde;uetele. </eesti>
<inglise>The supervisory board may refuse to grant the status of an account administrator only if an account administrator fails to comply with the requirements for account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud isikud peavad kogu kontohalduriks olemise aja v&auml;ltel vastama k&otilde;igile allj&auml;rgnevatele n&otilde;uetele: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Persons specified in subsection (2) of this section shall comply with all the following requirements during the whole period for which they are account administrators: </inglise>
<eesti>1) nende suhtes peab kehtima registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud leping, mille alusel nimetatud isikud on kohustunud tegutsema koosk&otilde;las k&auml;esoleva seaduse ning teiste Eesti Vabariigis kontohaldurite tegevust reguleerivate &otilde;igusaktidega, samuti registripidaja kehtestatud n&otilde;uetega; </eesti>
<inglise>1) they shall have a valid agreement with the registrar according to which the persons are required to act in compliance with this Act and other legislation regulating the activities of account administrators in the Republic of Estonia, and with the requirements established by the registrar; </inglise>
<eesti>2) t&auml;idetud peavad olema k&otilde;ik registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingus s&auml;testatud tagatiste seadmise ja kindlustuse kohustused; </eesti>
<inglise>2) all obligations concerning the provision of guarantees and insurance provided for in an agreement with the registrar are fulfilled; </inglise>
<eesti>3) registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud leping ning k&otilde;ik sellest tuleneda v&otilde;ivad vaidlused peavad olema allutatud Eesti Vabariigi &otilde;igusele ning Eesti Vabariigi kohtutele v&otilde;i vahekohtutele; </eesti>
<inglise>3) an agreement entered into with the registrar and all disputes which may arise therefrom are subject to the law of the Republic of Estonia and to the courts or arbitral tribunals of the Republic of Estonia; </inglise>
<eesti>4) registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud leping peab andma huvitatud isikutele iseseisva hagemise &otilde;iguse k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud isikute suhtes seoses nende tegevusega kontohaldurina. </eesti>
<inglise>4) an agreement entered into with the registrar shall ensure that interested persons have the right to file an independent action against persons provided for in subsection (2) of this section in connection with their activities as account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 33. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 33. </inglise>
<eesti>Korralduste edastaja </eesti>
<inglise>Person communicating orders </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur on kohustatud tagama, et registripidajale annaks korraldusi, edastaks andmeid ning teeks p&auml;ringuid tema selleks p&auml;dev esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>An account administrator is required to ensure that orders, information and inquiries are communicated to the registrar by a competent representative of the account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur vastutab selle kohustuse rikkumisest tekkinud kahju eest. </eesti>
<inglise>Account administrators are liable for damage arising from violation of this obligation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>Korralduste andmine registritoimingute tegemiseks, andmete edastamine ja p&auml;ringute tegemine </eesti>
<inglise>Issuing of orders to perform register acts, and communication of information and inquiries </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduril on &otilde;igus t&auml;ita ainult nendelt isikutelt saadud korraldusi ja p&auml;ringuid, kes on &otilde;igustatud k&auml;sutama vastaval v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An account administrator has the right to execute the orders and inquiries of only such persons who are entitled to dispose of the securities registered in the corresponding securities account. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur on kohustatud kontrollima temale registritoimingu tegemiseks korralduse andnud v&otilde;i registriandmete kohta teavet k&uuml;siva isiku (korralduse andja) &otilde;igust k&auml;sutada vastaval v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontol registreeritud v&auml;&auml;rtpabereid ning identifitseerima iga sellise isiku. </eesti>
<inglise>An account administrator who receives an order for the performance of a register act or an inquiry concerning register information from a person (the issuer of an order) is required to verify the right of the person to dispose of the securities registered in the corresponding securities account, and to identify each such person. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui registritoimingu tegemiseks ei anna korraldust f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanik v&otilde;i juriidilisest isikust v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku seadustest tulenev esindaja isiklikult, peab korralduse tegemiseks antav volitus olema notariaalselt t&otilde;estatud v&otilde;i sisalduma v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru kutselise osalisega s&otilde;lmitud varavalitsemis- v&otilde;i muus sarnases lepingus. </eesti>
<inglise>If an order for the performance of a register act is not issued personally by the owner of a securities account who is a natural person or by the legal representative of the owner of a securities account who is a legal person, the authorisation necessary for the issue of the order shall be notarised or included in a property administration contract or other such agreement entered into with a professional securities market participant. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohaldur on kohustatud t&auml;itma v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku, kohtut&auml;ituri ja pankrotihalduri seaduslikke korraldusi. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An account administrator is required to execute the legal orders of the owners of securities accounts, bailiffs and trustees in bankruptcy. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohalduril on keelatud edastada registripidajale korraldusi registritoimingu tegemiseks ilma v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku v&otilde;i tema poolt n&otilde;uetekohaselt volitatud isiku vastavasisulise korralduseta, kui seadusega ei ole s&auml;testatud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Unless otherwise provided by law, an account administrator shall not communicate orders for the performance of register acts to the registrar without a corresponding order from the owner of a securities account or the person duly authorised by the owner. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kontohaldur peab kontrollima tema poolt registripidajale edastatavate andmete &otilde;igsust. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) An account administrator shall verify the correctness of the information it communicates to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohaldur vastutab tema poolt registripidajale registritoimingu tegemiseks edastatud korralduste &otilde;igsuse ning korralduse andja tahtele vastavuse eest nii v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omaniku, tema poolt volitatud isiku kui ka registripidaja ees. </eesti>
<inglise>An account administrator is liable to the owner of a securities account, the persons authorised thereby and the registrar for the correctness of the orders it communicates to the registrar for the performance of register acts and for the correspondence of the orders to the intention of the issuers of the orders. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Registripidaja v&otilde;ib v&otilde;tta t&auml;itmiseks registritoimingute tegemiseks antud korraldusi ja p&auml;ringuid, mis on registripidajale n&otilde;uetekohaselt edastatud kontohalduri poolt kirjalikult v&otilde;i kirjalikku taasesitamist v&otilde;imaldavas vormis. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The registrar may accept for execution orders for the performance of register acts and inquiries communicated to the registrar by an account administrator according to the requirements and in writing or in a form enabling written reproduction. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kontohaldur on kohustatud s&auml;ilitama k&otilde;igi temale registritoimingute ja p&auml;ringute tegemiseks antud korralduste aluseks olevaid dokumente v&auml;hemalt k&uuml;mne aasta jooksul, arvates korralduse andmisest temale. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) An account administrator is required to preserve all documents which were the basis for orders issued thereto for the performance of register acts or inquiries for at least ten years as of the date of issue of the orders. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 35. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse peatamine </eesti>
<inglise>Suspension of status of account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Otilde;igusaktides v&otilde;i registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingus s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete rikkumise korral kontohalduri staatuses tegutseva isiku poolt, samuti tema mittevastavuse korral &otilde;igusaktides v&otilde;i registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingus s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele, on registripidaja n&otilde;ukogul &otilde;igus otsustada kontohalduri staatuses tegutsemise t&auml;ielik v&otilde;i osaline peatamine, kui see on vajalik, et kaitsta v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanike &otilde;igusi. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If a person with the status of an account administrator violates the requirements provided by legislation or an agreement with the registrar or fails to comply with the requirements provided by legislation or an agreement with the registrar, the supervisory board of the registrar has the right to decide to suspend the person's activities as an account administrator totally or partially if this is necessary to protect the rights of the owners of securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri staatuse t&auml;ielikust v&otilde;i osalisest peatamisest tulenevad piirangud t&uuml;histab registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu p&auml;rast kontohalduri staatuse peatamise tinginud asjaolude k&otilde;rvaldamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Restrictions arising from a total or partial suspension of the status of an account administrator shall be abolished by the supervisory board of the registrar after elimination of the circumstances which caused the suspension. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohalduri staatuse peatamise t&auml;psem kord m&auml;&auml;ratakse registripidamise korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A detailed procedure for the suspension of the status of an account administrator shall be established by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 36. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 36. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamine </eesti>
<inglise>Revocation of status of account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Otilde;igusaktides v&otilde;i registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingus s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete olulise rikkumise korral kontohalduri staatuses tegutseva isiku poolt, samuti tema mittevastavuse korral &otilde;igusaktides v&otilde;i registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingus s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele, on registripidaja n&otilde;ukogul &otilde;igus t&uuml;histada kontohalduri staatus, kui n&otilde;udeid rikkunud v&otilde;i n&otilde;uetele mittevastava isiku tegutsemine kontohaldurina on v&otilde;imatu v&otilde;i kui see kujutaks otsest ohtu v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanike &otilde;igustele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If a person with the status of an account administrator materially violates the requirements provided by legislation or an agreement with the registrar or fails to comply with the requirements provided by legislation or an agreement with the registrar, the supervisory board of the registrar has the right to revoke the person's status as an account administrator if it is impossible for the person who violated or failed to comply with the requirements to act as an account administrator or if it would constitute an immediate danger to the rights of owners of securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamisel korraldab registripidaja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode haldamis&otilde;iguse &uuml;leandmise kontohalduri staatuses tegutsemise &otilde;igust omavatele isikutele. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the status of an account administrator is revoked, the registrar shall organise the transfer of the right to administer securities accounts to persons holding the right to act as account administrators. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Haldamis&otilde;igus antakse &uuml;le registripidaja n&otilde;ukogu otsusega, milles m&auml;rgitakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Administration rights shall be transferred by a resolution of the supervisory board of the registrar which shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) haldamis&otilde;iguse &uuml;lemineku aeg; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the time of the transfer of administration rights; </inglise>
<eesti>2) muud tingimused ja asjaolud, mis on vajalikud haldamis&otilde;iguse &uuml;leandmise korraldamiseks viisil, millega tagatakse v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode omanikele v&otilde;imalus s&otilde;lmida kokkuleppeid v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode kasutamiseks uue kontohalduri vahendusel. </eesti>
<inglise>2) other conditions and circumstances necessary to organise the transfer of administration rights so as to ensure that owners of securities accounts have the opportunity to enter into agreements for the use of their securities accounts through a new account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise korral on kontohaldur kohustatud h&uuml;vitama k&otilde;igile tema vahendusel v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avanud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikele k&otilde;ik selliste v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode sulgemise, uute v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode avamise ning v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite suletavatelt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodelt uutele v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodele &uuml;lekandmisega seotud otsesed kulutused. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If the status of an account administrator is revoked, the account administrator is required to compensate all owners of securities accounts who have opened a securities account through such account administrator for all direct expenses related to the closure of such securities accounts, opening of new securities accounts and transfer of securities from closed securities accounts to new securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud otsus avaldatakse ametlikus v&auml;ljaandes Ametlikud Teadaanded ja viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul &uuml;ldsusele avatud arvutis&uuml;steemis. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A resolution specified in subsection (3) of this section shall be published in the official publication Ametlikud Teadaanded and, within five working days, in a computer system available to the public. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kontohalduri staatuse t&uuml;histamise t&auml;psem kord m&auml;&auml;ratakse registripidamise korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) A detailed procedure for the revocation of the status of an account administrator shall be established by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 37. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 37. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri staatusest loobumine </eesti>
<inglise>Waiver of status of account administrator </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduril on &otilde;igus loobuda kontohalduri staatusest, l&otilde;petades selleks registripidajaga s&otilde;lmitud lepingu, kui ta teatab sellest kirjalikult registripidajale v&auml;hemalt kaks kuud ette. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An account administrator has the right to waive the status of an account administrator by terminating the corresponding agreement with the registrar if the account administrator notifies the registrar of the waiver in writing at least two months in advance. </inglise>
<eesti>Kuni kontohalduri staatuse l&otilde;ppemise p&auml;evani kehtivad kontohalduri suhtes k&otilde;ik kontohalduri staatusest tulenevad &otilde;igused ja kohustused. </eesti>
<inglise>Until the date of termination of the status of an account administrator, all rights and obligations arising from the status of an account administrator apply with regard to the account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri staatusest loobuda sooviv kontohaldur on kohustatud teavitama sellest kirjalikult k&otilde;iki isikuid, kellel on tema vahendusel avatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontod. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An account administrator who wishes to waive the status of an account administrator is required to give written notice of the waiver to all persons who have opened a securities account through the account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastav teade peab olema saadetud t&auml;htkirjaga selliselt, et see oleks adressaadil k&auml;es v&auml;hemalt &uuml;ks kuu enne kontohalduri ning registripidaja vahelise lepingu l&otilde;ppemist. </eesti>
<inglise>The notice shall be sent by registered letter to be received by the addressee at least one month before termination of the agreement between the account administrator and the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>Lisaks teabele kontohalduri staatusest loobumise ja selle j&otilde;ustumise kuup&auml;eva kohta peab teade sisaldama k&otilde;igi teiste registripidaja kontohaldurite kontaktandmeid. </eesti>
<inglise>In addition to information concerning the waiver of the status of an account administrator and the date of entry into force thereof, the notice shall contain the details of all other account administrators of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontohalduri staatusest loobunud kontohaldur on kohustatud h&uuml;vitama k&otilde;igile tema vahendusel v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto avanud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikele k&otilde;ik selliste v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode sulgemise, uute v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode avamise ning v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite suletavatelt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodelt uutele v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontodele &uuml;lekandmisega seotud otsesed kulutused. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An account administrator who waives the status of an account administrator is required to compensate all owners of securities accounts who have opened a securities account through the account administrator for all direct expenses related to the closure of such securities accounts, opening of new securities accounts and transfer of securities from closed securities accounts to new securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>Kulutuste h&uuml;vitamise &otilde;igus tuleb &auml;ra n&auml;idata kontohalduri poolt v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanikele saadetavas teates kontohalduri staatusest loobumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>The right for compensation of expenses shall be indicated in the notice concerning waiver of the status of an account administrator sent by the account administrator to owners of securities accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) V&auml;hemalt &uuml;ks kuu enne lepingu l&otilde;ppemist on kontohaldur kohustatud avaldama sellekohase teate ametlikus v&auml;ljaandes Ametlikud Teadaanded ja &uuml;ldsusele avatud arvutis&uuml;steemis. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) At least one month before termination of the agreement, an account administrator is required to publish a corresponding notice in the official publication Ametlikud Teadaanded and a computer system available to the public. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kontohalduri staatusest loobumise t&auml;psem kord m&auml;&auml;ratakse registripidamise korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A detailed procedure for waiver of the status of an account administrator shall be established by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>6. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 6 </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 38. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 38. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve alused </eesti>
<inglise>Bases for supervision </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalvet registripidaja, kontohaldurite ja emitentide tegevuse &uuml;le teostab Finantsinspektsioon (edaspidi j&auml;relevalve teostaja) k&auml;esolevas seaduses ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberituru seaduses s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Supervision over the activities of the registrar, account administrators and issuers shall be exercised by the Financial Supervision Authority (hereinafter supervisory authority), pursuant to the procedure provided by this Act and the Securities Market Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalvet krediidiasutustest kontohaldurite tegevuse &uuml;le teostab Finantsinspektsioon (edaspidi j&auml;relevalve teostaja) krediidiasutuste seaduses, k&auml;esolevas seaduses ja nendest tulenevates &otilde;igusaktides s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Supervision over the activities of account administrators who are credit institutions shall be exercised by the Financial Supervision Authority (hereinafter supervisory authority), pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Credit Institutions Act, this Act and legislation arising therefrom. </inglise>
<eesti>(09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>(09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Vajaduse korral kaasatakse j&auml;relevalve teostamiseks s&otilde;ltumatuid eksperte ning tehakse koost&ouml;&ouml;d teiste Eesti ja v&auml;lismaiste j&auml;relevalveorganitega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If necessary, independent experts shall be engaged and co-operation shall take place with other Estonian and foreign supervisory authorities in order to exercise supervision. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 39. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 39. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve teostaja &uuml;lesanded </eesti>
<inglise>Duties of supervisory authorities </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve teostaja: </eesti>
<inglise>A supervisory authority shall: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kontrollib registripidaja ja kontohalduri tegevuse vastavust seadustele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) verify compliance of the activities of the registrar and account administrators with legislation; </inglise>
<eesti>2) annab seadusega etten&auml;htud heakskiite ja koosk&otilde;lastusi; </eesti>
<inglise>2) grant approval as prescribed by law; </inglise>
<eesti>3) teeb vajaduse korral k&auml;esolevast seadusest tulenevate n&otilde;uete rikkumise l&otilde;petamiseks registripidajale v&otilde;i kontohaldurile t&auml;itmiseks kohustuslikke ettekirjutusi; </eesti>
<inglise>3) issue, if necessary, mandatory precepts to the registrar or account administrators for termination of violations of requirements arising from this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>4) koostab protokollid k&auml;esoleva seaduse ja sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide rikkumise kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>4) prepare reports concerning violations of this Act or legislation arising therefrom; </inglise>
<eesti>5) t&auml;idab muid seadustest ja teistest &otilde;igusaktidest tulenevaid &uuml;lesandeid. </eesti>
<inglise>5) perform other duties arising from Acts or other legislation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 40. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 40. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutus </eesti>
<inglise>Precepts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 39 punktis 3 nimetatud ettekirjutuses peavad sisalduma: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A precept specified in clause 39 3) of this Act shall set out: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ettekirjutuse teinud j&auml;relevalve teostaja ametiisiku nimi ja ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name and position of the official of the supervisory authority who prepared the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>2) ettekirjutuse tegemise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the date of preparation of the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>3) ettekirjutuse saaja nimi ja aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the name and address of the recipient of the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>4) ettekirjutuse tegemise alused koos viitega vastavatele seaduss&auml;tetele; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the bases for issue of the precept together with a reference to the relevant provisions of legislation; </inglise>
<eesti>5) ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmise t&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the term for compliance with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>6) ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmisel rakendatavad sanktsioonid. </eesti>
<inglise>6) the sanctions to be imposed upon failure to comply with the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Ettekirjutus v&auml;ljastatakse viivitamata registripidaja v&otilde;i kontohalduri esindajale allkirja vastu. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A precept shall be issued promptly to the representative of the registrar or the account administrator against a signature. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Ettekirjutuse saaja peab p&auml;rast ettekirjutuse saamist viivitamata asuma selle t&auml;itmisele. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The recipient of a precept shall commence compliance with the precept promptly after receipt thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ettekirjutuse saajal on 15 p&auml;eva jooksul p&auml;rast ettekirjutuse saamist &otilde;igus vaidlustada see kohtus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A recipient of a precept has the right to file an action against the precept in a court within fifteen days after receipt of the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutuse vaidlustamine kohtus ei peata selle t&auml;itmise kohustust, kui seadusega ei s&auml;testata teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>Filing an action against a precept in court does not suspend the requirement to comply therewith unless otherwise provided by law. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 41. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 41. </inglise>
<eesti>Kohapealne kontroll </eesti>
<inglise>On-site inspection </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalve teostajal on &otilde;igus registripidaja juures l&auml;bi viia kohapealset kontrolli. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The supervisory authority has the right to conduct on-site inspections of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kohapealsel kontrollimisel on registripidaja kohustatud j&auml;relevalve teostaja poolt volitatud isikul (kontrollijal) v&otilde;imaldama piiranguteta tutvuda registripidaja tegevust kajastavate dokumentide ja failidega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon on-site inspection, the registrar is required to enable the person authorised by the supervisory authority (inspector) to examine documents and files concerning the activities of the registrar without restrictions. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kontrollijatel on &otilde;igus teha dokumentidest ja failidest v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid, &auml;rakirju ja koopiaid. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Inspectors have the right to make copies and transcripts of and extracts from documents and files. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kontrollija on kohustatud koostama kontrollimise kohta akti, milles tuleb m&auml;rkida k&otilde;ik dokumendid ja failid, millega kontrollija kohapealse kontrolli k&auml;igus tutvus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) An inspector is required to prepare a report concerning an inspection setting out all documents and files examined by the inspector in the course of the on-site inspection. </inglise>
<eesti>Akt esitatakse tutvumiseks registripidaja juhatusele. </eesti>
<inglise>The report shall be submitted to the management board of the registrar for review. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja esindaja annab aktile sellega tutvumise kohta allkirja. </eesti>
<inglise>The representative of the registrar shall sign the report to confirm that it has been reviewed. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui registripidaja esindaja keeldub aktile alla kirjutamast, tehakse sellesse vastav kanne. </eesti>
<inglise>If the representative of the registrar refuses to sign the report, a corresponding entry shall be made in the report. </inglise>
<eesti>Aktile lisatakse registripidaja esindaja kirjalikud m&auml;rkused akti, samuti aktile allakirjutamisest keeldumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>Written comments of the representative of the registrar concerning the report or refusal to sign the report shall be annexed to the report. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 42. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 42. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve teostajale teabe esitamise kohustus </eesti>
<inglise>Obligation to provide information to supervisory authority </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja ja kontohaldur peavad viivitamata teatama j&auml;relevalve teostajale k&otilde;igist oma tegevust ja finantsseisundit oluliselt m&otilde;jutavatest asjaoludest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar and account administrators shall promptly notify the supervisory agency of all circumstances which materially affect their activities or financial situation. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui registripidaja v&otilde;i kontohalduri tegevus ei vasta &otilde;igusaktides v&otilde;i p&otilde;hikirjas s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele, on registripidaja ja kontohaldur kohustatud sellest ja tekkinud olukorra lahendamiseks kavandatud abin&otilde;udest viivitamata teatama j&auml;relevalve teostajale. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the activities of the registrar or an account administrator do not comply with the requirements provided by legislation or their articles of association, the registrar or the account administrator is required to notify the supervisory authority promptly thereof and of measures envisaged to deal with the situation. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Registripidaja ja kontohaldur peavad j&auml;relevalve teostaja n&otilde;udel k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud asjaolud v&otilde;i k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud abin&otilde;ud viivitamata avalikustama. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) At the request of the supervisory authority, the registrar or an account administrator shall promptly disclose to the public the circumstances specified in subsection (1) of this section or the measures specified in subsection (2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Esindajakonto omanik peab k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 6 l&otilde;ikes 7 nimetatud andmed n&otilde;udmisel avaldama j&auml;relevalve teostajale, samuti Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri pidajale. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Owners of nominee accounts shall disclose information specified in subsection 6 (7) of this Act to a supervisory authority or the registrar of the Estonian Central Register of Securities at their request. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidamise korras v&otilde;ib andmete v&auml;ljastamiseks kehtestada t&auml;psema korra. </eesti>
<inglise>A more detailed procedure for the release of information may be established by the procedure for maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Esindajakonto omanik on kohustatud teavitama kontohaldurit ja j&auml;relevalve teostajat sellest, kui tulenevalt esindajakontol olevatest v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest h&auml;&auml;leenamus v&otilde;i muu osalus nimetatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberid emiteerinud &auml;ri&uuml;hingus &uuml;letab v&otilde;i langeb alla &otilde;igusaktis s&auml;testatud piiri, millega kaasneb &otilde;igusaktist tulenev kohustus teavitada nimetatud asjaolust, kohustus taotleda riigiasutuselt selleks luba v&otilde;i kohustus teha teatud toiminguid. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The owner of a nominee account is required to notify the account administrator and the supervisory authority if, due to the securities in the nominee account, a majority or any other holding in the company which issued the securities exceeds or falls below a threshold provided by legislation, resulting in the obligation arising from legislation to give notice of such circumstances, the obligation to apply for corresponding authorisation from a state agency or the obligation to perform certain acts. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Teavitamise kohustus k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 5 s&auml;testatu t&auml;henduses on esindajakonto omanikul ka juhul, kui h&auml;&auml;leenamus v&otilde;i muu osalus suureneb v&otilde;i v&auml;heneb esindajakonto omaniku poolt hoitavatest v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest ja esindajakonto omaniku kui kontohalduri poolt peetavatel kontodel hoitavatest v&auml;&auml;rtpaberitest tulenevalt. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The notification obligation within the meaning of the provisions of subsection (5) of this section also applies to the owner of a nominee account if a majority or other holding increases or decreases as a result of securities held by the owner of the nominee account or securities in accounts held by the owner of the nominee account as an account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 43. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 43. </inglise>
<eesti>&Otilde;igus saada teavet kolmandatelt isikutelt </eesti>
<inglise>Right to obtain information from third persons </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve teostajal on k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmiseks &otilde;igus: </eesti>
<inglise>In order to perform the duties provided for in this Act, the supervisory authority has the right: </inglise>
<eesti>1) saada registripidaja tegevuse kohta teavet kontohalduritelt, Eesti Pangalt, riigi andmekogude vastutavatelt ja volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejatelt, registripidaja likvideerijatelt v&otilde;i pankrotihalduritelt; </eesti>
<inglise>1) to obtain information concerning the activities of the registrar from account administrators, the Bank of Estonia, the chief processors and authorised processors of state databases, and the liquidators and trustees in bankruptcy of the registrar; </inglise>
<eesti>2) saada kontohalduri tegevuse kohta teavet registripidajalt, teistelt kontohalduritelt, Eesti Pangalt, riigi andmekogude vastutavatelt ja volitatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlejatelt, kontohalduri likvideerijatelt v&otilde;i pankrotihalduritelt; </eesti>
<inglise>2) to obtain information concerning the activities of an account administrator from the registrar, other account administrators, the Bank of Estonia, the chief processors and authorised processors of state databases, and the liquidators and trustees in bankruptcy of the account administrator; </inglise>
<eesti>3) n&otilde;uda k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi punktides 1 ja 2 nimetatud isikute k&auml;sutuses olevate registripidaja v&otilde;i kontohalduri kohta k&auml;ivate dokumentide esitamist. </eesti>
<inglise>3) to demand the submission of documents concerning the registrar or an account administrator which are at the disposal of persons specified in clauses 1) and 2) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 44. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 44. </inglise>
<eesti>Juhtimisorganite kokkukutsumine </eesti>
<inglise>Calling meetings of management bodies </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalve teostajal on &otilde;igus v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikonto omanike huvide kaitseks teha registripidajale ettekirjutus n&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;i aktsion&auml;ride &uuml;ldkoosoleku kokkukutsumiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order to protect the interests of the owners of securities accounts, the supervisory authority has the right to issue a precept to the registrar to call a meeting of the supervisory board or a general meeting of the shareholders of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) J&auml;relevalve teostajal on &otilde;igus saata registripidaja aktsion&auml;ride &uuml;ldkoosolekule ning k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud juhul ka n&otilde;ukogu koosolekule oma esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The supervisory authority has the right to send a representative thereof to a general meeting of the shareholders of the registrar and, in the case specified in subsection (1) of this section, also to a meeting of the supervisory board of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 45. (Kehtetu - 09.05.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 45. (Repealed - 09.05.2001 entered into force 01.01.2002 - RT I 2001, 48, 268) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 46. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 46. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidajapoolne j&auml;relevalve kontohalduri tegevuse &uuml;le </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision by registrar of activities of account administrators </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidajal on &otilde;igus kontrollida kontohalduri tegevuse vastavust kehtivate &otilde;igusaktide ja registripidaja kehtestatud n&otilde;uetele registripidaja ja kontohalduri vahel s&otilde;lmitud lepingutes etten&auml;htud tingimustel ja korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar has the right to verify the compliance of the activities of an account administrator with the requirements of legislation in force and requirements established by the registrar, under the conditions and pursuant to the procedure prescribed by agreements between the registrar and the account administrator. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidajale laieneb krediidiasutuste seaduses s&auml;testatud pangasaladuse hoidmise kohustus. </eesti>
<inglise>The obligation to maintain the confidentiality of information subject to banking secrecy, provided by the Credit Institutions Act, extends to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohaldur on kohustatud esitama kontrolli l&auml;biviivale registripidaja t&ouml;&ouml;tajale k&otilde;ik viimase n&otilde;utud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontode avamise ning registritoimingute ja p&auml;ringute tegemise aluseks olevad ning nendega seotud dokumendid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) At the request of an employee of the registrar conducting an inspection, an account administrator is required to submit to the latter all documents which were the basis for or relate to the opening of securities accounts or the performance of register acts and inquiries. </inglise>
<eesti>7. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 7 </inglise>
<eesti>Vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Liability </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 47. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 47. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja haldusvastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja poolt vale teabe esitamise, samuti kohustuslike dokumentide ja teabe esitamata v&otilde;i avaldamata j&auml;tmise, mittet&auml;ieliku v&otilde;i mitte&otilde;igeaegse esitamise v&otilde;i avaldamise eest v&otilde;i seadusega etten&auml;htud registritoimingute tegemata j&auml;tmise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 1 000 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A fine of up to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed on the registrar for submission of incorrect information, for failure to submit or disclose mandatory documents or information, for failure to submit or disclose mandatory documents or information in full or on time, and for failure to perform register acts prescribed by law. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja poolt j&auml;relevalve teostaja ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise v&otilde;i selle mitte&otilde;igeaegse v&otilde;i mittet&auml;ieliku t&auml;itmise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 100 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A fine of up to 100 000 kroons shall be imposed on the registrar for failure to comply with a precept of the supervisory authority or for failure to comply on time or in full therewith. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 48. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 48. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri haldusvastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability of account administrators </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohalduri poolt vale teabe esitamise, samuti kohustuslike dokumentide ja teabe esitamata v&otilde;i avaldamata j&auml;tmise, mittet&auml;ieliku v&otilde;i mitte&otilde;igeaegse esitamise v&otilde;i avaldamise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 1 000 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A fine of up to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed on an account administrator for submission of incorrect information, for failure to submit or disclose mandatory documents or information and for failure to submit or disclose mandatory documents or information in full or on time. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohalduri poolt ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise v&otilde;i selle mitte&otilde;igeaegse v&otilde;i mittet&auml;ieliku t&auml;itmise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 500 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A fine of up to 500 000 kroons shall be imposed on an account administrator for failure to comply with a precept or for failure to comply on time or in full therewith. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Isikule, kes vastava &otilde;igusliku aluseta tegutseb kontohaldurina - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 1 000 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A fine of up to 1 000 000 kroons shall be imposed on a person who acts as an account administrator without a due legal basis. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Trahvi m&auml;&auml;rajal on &otilde;igus k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi kohaselt m&auml;&auml;ratud trahvidest teavitada ajakirjandust. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The person imposing a fine has the right to notify the press of fines imposed pursuant to this section. </inglise>
<eesti>Teates peab olema m&auml;rgitud selle kontohalduri nimi, kellele trahv m&auml;&auml;rati, ning trahvi m&auml;&auml;ramise p&otilde;hjus ja kuup&auml;ev. </eesti>
<inglise>A notice shall set out the name of the account administrator on which a fine is imposed and the reason for and date of imposition of the fine. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 49. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 49. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldusvastutus registripidajale andmete esitamata j&auml;tmise eest </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability for failure to submit information to registrar </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidajale seadusega s&auml;testatud andmete esitamata j&auml;tmise, muu hulgas v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registris registreerimata j&auml;tmise eest, kui selline kohustus on seadusega s&auml;testatud, v&otilde;i valeandmete esitamise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 2 000 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>A fine of up to 2 000 000 kroons shall be imposed for failure to submit information provided by law to the registrar, including failure to enter securities in the register of securities if such requirement is provided by law, and for submission of false information to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 50. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 50. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise protokolli koostamine </eesti>
<inglise>Preparation of administrative offence reports </inglise>
<eesti>(1) J&auml;relevalve teostaja volitatud ametiisikul on &otilde;igus koostada protokoll registripidaja v&otilde;i kontohalduri toimepandud rikkumise kohta v&otilde;i k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 49 nimetatud rikkumiste kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An official authorised by the supervisory authority has the right to prepare reports on violations committed by the registrar or account administrators, and on violations specified in &sect; 49 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud protokollis peavad sisalduma j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A report specified in subsection (1) of this section shall set out the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) koostamise aeg ja koht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the time and place of preparation of the report; </inglise>
<eesti>2) m&auml;rge selle kohta, et protokoll on koostatud j&auml;relevalve teostaja nimel; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a notation indicating that the report is prepared in the name of the supervisory authority; </inglise>
<eesti>3) protokolli koostanud isiku ametinimetus ja nimi; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the official title and name of the person who prepared the report; </inglise>
<eesti>4) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja &auml;rinimi, asukoht ja v&otilde;imaluse korral registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the business name, seat and, if possible, registry code of the administrative offender; </inglise>
<eesti>5) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja nimi ja ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the name and position of the representative of the administrative offender; </inglise>
<eesti>6) haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise koht, aeg ja kirjeldus; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the place, time and description of the administrative offence; </inglise>
<eesti>7) viide seaduss&auml;tetele, mille alusel haldusvastutust kohaldatakse; </eesti>
<inglise>7) a reference to the provisions of legislation which are the basis for imposition of administrative liability; </inglise>
<eesti>8) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja seletus v&otilde;i m&auml;rge seletuse andmisest loobumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>8) an explanation provided by the representative of the administrative offender or a notation concerning refusal to provide an explanation. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Protokollile kirjutavad alla selle koostanud isik ja haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The person who prepares a report and the representative of the administrative offender shall sign the report. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja keeldub protokollile alla kirjutamast, tehakse sellesse vastav kanne. </eesti>
<inglise>If the representative of the administrative offender refuses to sign the report, a corresponding entry shall be made in the report. </inglise>
<eesti>Protokollile lisatakse haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja kirjalikud m&auml;rkused protokolli, samuti protokollile allakirjutamisest keeldumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>Written notations made by the representative of the administrative offender concerning the report or refusal to sign the report shall be annexed to the report. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 51. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 51. </inglise>
<eesti>Menetlus haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise asjas </eesti>
<inglise>Proceedings in matters concerning administrative offence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Menetlus k&auml;esoleva seaduse rikkumise asjas registripidaja, emitendi v&otilde;i kontohalduri poolt, sealhulgas sanktsioonide rakendamine ja nende vaidlustamine, toimub haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 50, 548; 58, 608; 60, 616; 87, 792; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 45, 279; 49, 301; 305; 51, 321; 54, 346; 348; 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544; 548; 89, 578; 95, 609; 613; 2001, 3, 5; 9, 41; 17, 76; 18, 87; 21, 115; 116; 31, 174; 42, 236; 52, 303; 53, 312; 313; 314; 56, 333; 335; 339; 58, 356) menetluskorda j&auml;rgides. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Proceedings, including the imposition of sanctions and appeals against such sanctions, in matters concerning violation of this Act by the registrar, an issuer or an account administrator shall be conducted pursuant to the procedure established by the Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 50, 548; 58, 608; 60, 616; 87, 792; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 45, 279; 49, 301; 305; 51, 321; 54, 346; 348; 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544; 548; 89, 578; 95, 609; 613; 2001, 3, 5; 9, 41; 17, 76; 18, 87; 21, 115; 116; 31, 174; 42, 236; 52, 303; 53, 312; 313; 314; 56, 333; 335; 339; 58, 356). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse rikkumise asja arutamise ja karistuse m&auml;&auml;ramise &otilde;igus on halduskohtunikul ja j&auml;relevalve teostaja p&auml;deval ametiisikul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Administrative court judges and competent officials of a supervisory authority have the right to hear matters concerning and impose punishments for violations of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve teostaja p&auml;deval ametiisikul on &otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;rata rahatrahv kuni 50 000 krooni ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>Competent officials of a supervisory authority have the right to impose fines of up to 50 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel m&auml;&auml;ratud rahatrahv n&otilde;utakse sisse haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus ja t&auml;itemenetluse seadustikus (RT I 1993, 49, 693; 2001, 29, 156; 43, 238) kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Fines imposed on the basis of this Act shall be collected pursuant to the procedure established by the Code of Administrative Offences and the Code of Enforcement Procedure (RT I 1993, 49, 693; 2001, 29, 156; 43, 238). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 52. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 52. </inglise>
<eesti>Registripidaja tsiviilvastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Civil liability of registrar </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Registripidaja peab h&uuml;vitama registripidamisel oma kohustuste rikkumisega tekitatud kahju. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The registrar shall compensate for damage caused by violation of the obligations thereof in the maintenance of the register. </inglise>
<eesti>Kahju h&uuml;vitamise kohustust ei ole, kui kohustuse rikkumine toimus registripidajast s&otilde;ltumatutel asjaoludel. </eesti>
<inglise>The obligation to compensate for damage does not apply if obligations were violated under circumstances independent of the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 30 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud kohustuse rikkumise eest vastutab registripidaja, olenemata tema s&uuml;&uuml;st. </eesti>
<inglise>The registrar, whether guilty or not, is liable for violation of the obligation provided for in subsection 30 (1) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Registripidaja peab kindlustama registripidamisest ja muust tegevusest tuleneva vastutuse. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The registrar shall insure liability arising from the maintenance of the register and other activities. </inglise>
<eesti>Kindlustuslepingu p&otilde;hitingimused tuleb eelnevalt koosk&otilde;lastada rahandusministriga. </eesti>
<inglise>The principal conditions of the insurance contract shall be previously approved by the Minister of Finance. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui kahju h&uuml;vitamise n&otilde;udeid ei ole v&otilde;imalik rahuldada k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1 ja 2 s&auml;testatud viisil v&otilde;i seda ei ole v&otilde;imalik teha t&auml;ies ulatuses, vastutab tekkinud kahju eest Eesti Vabariik, kellel on tagasin&otilde;ude &otilde;igus registripidaja vastu. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If claims for damages cannot be satisfied pursuant to subsections (1) and (2) of this section or if such claims cannot be satisfied in full, the Republic of Estonia is liable for the damage caused and has the right of recourse to the registrar. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 53. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 53. </inglise>
<eesti>Kontohalduri tsiviilvastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Professional liability of account administrators </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kontohaldur vastutab konto haldamisega seotud kohustuste rikkumise eest &uuml;ldistel alustel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An account administrator bears liability for violation of obligations relating to the administration of an account, pursuant to the general principles. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 31 l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatud kohustuse rikkumise eest vastutab kontohaldur, olenemata tema s&uuml;&uuml;st. </eesti>
<inglise>An account administrator, whether guilty or not, is liable for violation of the obligation provided for in subsection 31 (3) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kontohaldur peab kindlustama kontode haldamisest tuleneva vastutuse. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An account administrator shall insure the liability arising from administration of accounts. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui kahju h&uuml;vitamise n&otilde;udeid ei ole v&otilde;imalik rahuldada k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1 ja 2 s&auml;testatud viisil v&otilde;i seda ei ole v&otilde;imalik teha t&auml;ies ulatuses, vastutab tekkinud kahju eest Eesti Vabariik, kellel on tagasin&otilde;ude &otilde;igus kontohalduri vastu. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If claims for damages cannot be satisfied pursuant to subsections (1) and (2) of this section or if such claims cannot be satisfied in full, the Republic of Estonia is liable for the damage caused and has the right of recourse to the account administrator. </inglise>
