<inglise>Amendment of Commercial Code (RT I 1995, 26/28, 355; 1998, 91/93, 1500; 1999, 10, 155; 23, 355; 24, 360; 57, 596; 102, 907; 2000, 29, 172; 49, 303; 55, 365; 57, 373; 2001, 24, 133; 34, 185; 56, 332; 33) </inglise>
