<eesti>Seaduse j&otilde;ustumine </eesti>
<inglise>Entry into force of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 2001. aasta 1. jaanuaril. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act enters into force on 1 January 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajal olemasolevate ning k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 2 l&otilde;ike 1 punktides 1, 2, 4 ja 5 nimetatud v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite registreerimiseks Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistris tuleb esitada avaldus hiljemalt 2001. aasta 1. septembriks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An application for the entry of securities existing upon the entry into force of this Act and securities specified in clauses 2 (1) 1), 2), 4) and 5) of this Act in the Estonian Central Register of Securities shall be submitted not later than by 1 September 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajal olemasolevad aktsiaseltsid, samuti aktsiaseltsid, mida ei ole selleks ajaks veel &auml;riregistrisse kantud, kuid mille asutamisotsus on vastu v&otilde;etud v&otilde;i asutamisleping s&otilde;lmitud, peavad esitama taotluse oma aktsiate registreerimiseks Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistris hiljemalt 2003. aasta 1. jaanuariks. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Public limited companies existing upon the entry into force of this Act and public limited companies which are not entered in the commercial register by that time but whose foundation resolution has been adopted or whose memorandum of association has been concluded shall submit an application for the entry of their shares in the Estonian Central Register of Securities not later than by 1 January 2003. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Aktsiaseltsid, kelle aktsiaid emiteeritakse v&otilde;i pakutakse avalikult, peavad oma aktsiad enne nende avalikku emiteerimist v&otilde;i pakkumist registreerima Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistris. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Public limited companies whose shares are publicly issued or tendered shall enter their shares in the Estonian Central Register of Securities before the public issue or tender. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Aktsiaseltsid, kelle p&otilde;hikirjas on k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajal ette n&auml;htud v&otilde;imalus esitajaaktsiate v&auml;ljaandmiseks, peavad esitajaaktsiad vahetama nimelisteks, viima p&otilde;hikirja vastavusse k&auml;esolevas seaduses ja &auml;riseadustikus s&auml;testatuga ning esitama avalduse vastava p&otilde;hikirja muudatuse &auml;riregistrisse kandmiseks hiljemalt 2001. aasta 31. detsembriks. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Public limited companies whose articles of association, upon the entry into force of this Act, permit them to issue bearer shares shall exchange their bearer shares for registered shares, bring their articles of association into compliance with the provisions of this Act and the Commercial Code and submit an application for the entry of the corresponding amendments to their articles of association in the commercial register not later than by 31 December 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistri pidaja esitab &auml;riregistri pidajale 2002. aasta 1. veebruariks ja 2003. aasta 1. veebruariks andmed aktsiaseltside kohta, kelle aktsiad on registreeritud Eesti v&auml;&auml;rtpaberite keskregistris. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The registrar of the Estonian Central Register of Securities shall submit information to the registrar of the commercial register by 1 February 2002 and 1 February 2003 concerning public limited companies whose shares are entered in the Estonian Central Register of Securities. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 3 ja 5 nimetatud avalduse t&auml;htajaks esitamata j&auml;tmisel v&otilde;i avalduse rahuldamata j&auml;tmisel loetakse aktsiaselts sundl&otilde;petatuks. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) A public limited company which fails to submit an application specified in subsection (3) or (5) of this Act within the specified term or whose application is denied is deemed to have undergone compulsory dissolution. </inglise>
<eesti>(8) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 7 alusel sundl&otilde;petatuks loetud &auml;ri&uuml;hingule kohaldatakse &auml;riseadustiku &sect;-s 513 s&auml;testatut, kusjuures ettev&otilde;tteregistri asemel kasutatakse s&auml;tete kohaldamisel m&otilde;istet "&auml;riregister" ning nende s&auml;tetega ettev&otilde;tteregistri pidajale pandud kohustusi t&auml;idab &auml;riregistri pidaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) The provisions of section 513 of the Commercial Code apply to companies deemed to have undergone compulsory dissolution pursuant to subsection (7) of this section; the term "commercial register" shall be used instead of enterprise register upon application of the provisions, and the duties assigned to the registrar of the enterprise register by the given provisions shall be performed by the registrar of the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Kuni esitajaaktsiate &uuml;mbervahetamiseni v&otilde;i esitajaaktsiatega aktsiaseltsi l&otilde;ppemiseni kohaldatakse esitajaaktsiatele &auml;riseadustikus esitajaaktsiate kohta kuni k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumiseni kehtinud s&auml;tteid. </eesti>
<inglise>(9) Until the exchange of bearer shares or the dissolution of a public limited company which has issued bearer shares, the provisions of the Commercial Code applicable to bearer shares until the entry into force of this Act apply to bearer shares. </inglise>
